descr: An innocent & lovable youngster who lives a carefree life. He likes to drink tea on most days and often makes recommendations to the people around him. However, his friends tend to avoid his recommendations as they are usually quite horrible recommendations.
name: Long Bao

descr: Vanilla is the older brother while Strawberry is the younger brother. However, in most cases, Strawberry is usually the calm and collected one.
name: Double Scoop

descr: A standard businessman with very cohesive & strong leadership skills. His demeanor manages to attract many young women. He can be a little unpredictable.
name: Coffee

descr: Although he has the appearance of a young child, his real age is unknown. He hates people who give up easily. He enjoys sitting underneath the trees while drinking alcohol till the sun rises.
name: Crab Long Bao

descr: An optimistic young boy that can often be seen walking around with a giant smile on his face! He also likes to carry his fish around! His optimism is contagious and makes everyone happy!
name: Sashimi

descr: This is a woman who is always angry and agitated. It's best to leave her alone and avoid making contact with her.
name: Skewer

descr: An optimistic and bubbly young girl, she can often be seen wearing colorful costumes and smiling at everything. She enjoys being around her Master Attendant.
name: Macaron

descr: A young lady with a gentle, kind and clam personality. She is extremely caring and hopes that all those around her can find happiness.
name: Tiramisu

descr: A young lady who thinks of herself very highly. She likes to hold her fan up to her face to cover her smile. She enjoys shopping at discount stores and finding the best deals.
name: Crepe

descr: Extremely loyal to his Master Attendant. He is cautious and acts as an advisor to his Master Attendant.
name: Zongzi

descr: Aside from playing cards, he doesn't care much about anything else. His most important item are his playing cards.
name: Sandwich

descr: A very serious young woman. She treats all of her missions and tasks with the upmost pride and ensures that they are always completed to perfection. She spends her time on the training ground and carries her guns with her at all times. However, no one knows for sure where she comes from or who she really is.
name: Black Tea

descr: A cute and innocent young girl, she looks at the world with awe and curiosity. She's full of questions for you to answer! Be careful though, once you answer her, she'll never stop asking!
name: Hawthorne Ball

descr: A gentle and well-mannered scholar. He adores listening to the opera and singing classic tunes. His voice can often be heard echoing in the streets.
name: Plum Juice

descr: A young man with unique charm. He holds a bouquet of roses, ready to give one to anyone he admires. Don’t stare into his eyes for too long or you might fall madly in love with him.
name: Chocolate

descr: An optimistic young girl who hates seeing people sad. She enjoys making other people happy by summoning beautiful cherry blossoms to brighten up their day.
name: Sakuramochi

descr: A hot-blooded young man who is passionate about everything. Due to his strong sense of justice, he sees it as his mission to protect the weak. He has very good luck and will often turn misfortunes into blessings.
name: Tom Yum

descr: As long as she likes you, this young lady will do anything for you. It's a blessing and a curse to be loved by her; she'll do anything for you and she'll do everything to make you happy. She can often be found sunbathing on the beach.
name: Nasi Lemak

descr: She may seem overly enthusiastic at times but the people of Light Kingdom are extremely fond of her because of her character. When it comes to health, there's no one with better knowledge than her.
name: Yogurt

descr: He is overbearing, aggressive, and does not like being ordered around. The only way to make him smile is through violence and pain. However, he hates when his body gets hot and has gotten into the habit of undressing when this happens.
name: Boston Lobster

descr: A young girl with a lot of heart and vitality. Her sweet and beautiful singing voice can lift the spirits of even the saddest souls. She's also quite popular amongst everyone.
name: Jello

descr: She can bring good luck to others and is a symbol of good fortune. She likes to stick close to her brother and is especially fond of ceremonies.
name: Taiyaki

descr: A quiet and reserved Food Soul. When a friend is in danger she will come to their rescue. However, she's not very patient when it comes to dealing with everyday matters.
name: Milk

descr: This young and noble woman is like a queen; she holds herself in high regards and can be quite cold at times. Who knows? Maybe the right Master Attendant can melt her icy heart.
name: Foie Gras

descr: A drowsy-eyed youngster who is constantly sleeping. He always carries a pillow with him no matter where he is. The only party he likes is a sleepover party… I wonder why…
name: Escargot

descr: An extreme narcissist who likes to hold a warm and educated appearance in front of girls. He doesn't like other guys and can often be seen hanging around movie theaters… alone...
name: Popcorn

descr: She loves all the beauty in the world and is a talented painter. She is admired by many young people for her smooth hair and elegant facial features. However, she can also be quite stern and unforgiving at times.
name: Hotdog

descr: A young girl who is full of energy and is always busy. She is very fond of playing pranks on others. When she gets away with them, she will seem very proud of herself. However, if she is caught, she'll be very unhappy.
name: Moon Cake

descr: The elder brother of Taiyaki, he has the temperament of a child. He cherishes his younger sister very much and if anyone gets too close to her he will lose his temper.
name: Dorayaki

descr: A solemn young man who is inflexible and likes for everything to be in order. He is rather cold to those around him but is extremely attentive to Jello. He will always walk by her side & act as her escort.
name: Pudding

descr: She has the appearance of a pure, lovable and smart girl. She desires to become the most popular person in the room. She knows how to use her appearance to attract others.
name: Mango Pudding

descr: A man of few words who seldom interacts with others. However, if the topic of alcohol comes up then he will talk non-stop. He usually stays in his room and doesn't like to leave.
name: Sake

descr: He is candid and carefree with a passion for skateboarding. He likes to show off on the street and enjoys being admired. However, if you pay him a complement then he will be rather modest about it. He is confident when competing with other men but when it comes to girls, he seems to be completely lost.
name: Hamburger

descr: Incredibly enthusiastic and tough. He demands a lot from other and even more from himself. His passion and fire can throw people off at times.
name: Tempura

descr: She takes all matters very seriously and is rather direct which can upset people. It is because of her straightforward manner, she prefers to have her brother Sashimi communicate for her.
name: Sushi

descr: A young woman from the northern Slavic region. Most people cannot stand her stubbornness and uncompromising nature. She has the appearance of a cute and smart snow princess. But if you want to be with her, you must also win over her eagle.
name: Vodka

descr: A gentle young man. He is always smiling and is never without his pipe. He loves spending time with his ducks. He treats everyone with equality and respect. However, he can be a rather strange fellow at times.
name: Peking Duck

descr: A seductive young woman with strong desires. Her strong character and attractive figure often make others nervous when approaching her. She enjoys training and charming those around her.
name: Spicy Gluten

descr: He has incredible fighting strength and was born to battle. His grand status makes people think of him as somewhat arrogant. Whatever the issue, he prefers to use brute force to solve it. He hates Red Wine the most and frequently gets into physical conflicts with him.
name: Steak

descr: A young girl filled with passion and excitement. She is the symbol of fortune and good luck. Every year, during a special day, the people wait for her arrival as if fortune was coming their way.
name: Tangyuan

descr: A silent young man. He takes in and raises many homeless cats and prefers them over humans.
name: Sanma

descr: Frequently found wearing beautiful clothing, this young man is very kind. However, be careful of his sweet-talking mouth and flattery. He's known to be a bit of a womanizer.
name: Sukiyaki

descr: An earnest and stern youngster. His goal in life is to become a qualified butler. In fact, some people think of him as being far too reserved.
name: Brownie

descr: A white-eyed young girl who carries her fishing gear around with her. Just like a lovable daughter, she will listen to the Attendant's words. Sometimes the fish basket she carries will emit a faint white light. There seems to be an incredible force in there.
name: Cold Rice Shrimp

descr: A hard-nosed teacher who prefers not to help others but can't resist himself. He'll often find himself in situations that could have been avoided had he just walked away.
name: Tortoise Jelly

descr: A young man who lives alone in the jungle with animals for company. He enjoys hunting and is good at raising and training wild beasts. He is straightforward, simple, and pure. He gets excited when he runs into strangers.
name: Bamboo Rice

descr: An eccentric and mysterious young lady. She's not the easiest to get along with but this is only because she does not really understand how the world works. She's good at casting spells with great power.
name: Milt

descr: He doesn't really care about anything going on around him as he thinks it’s rather troublesome. However, sometimes he will be drawn into battle based on objective reasoning. Some people think of him as a fighting machine but all he wants to be seen is a normal person.
name: B-52

descr: Moody adolescents sometimes act out in strange ways to get people's attention. They may seem unreasonable, but they actually have their own principles that they adhere to. Since they're too self-conscious in their daily lives, they have a hard time communicating with other people.
name: Eclair

descr: A young man who is full of confidence. He is a lover of sweet treats and likes to dress in clothing from the Napoleonic Era. He is disgusted by anyone who tries to touch his hat.
name: Napoleon Cake

descr: A smart little girl who’s not very good at making new friends. She always appears very shy and prefers to keep to herself.
name: Jiuniang

descr: This Food Soul may seem carefree, but he is actually an extremely reliable person. Both he and Pancake have been sworn brothers since childhood and roam the world together.
name: Beggar's Chicken

descr: He is treated like nobility. He has the natural air of a king and his ruthless manner makes everyone around him feel a little inferior. Some Food Souls believe that this is all an act to hide his insecurities.
name: Spaghetti

descr: Jello's number one fan! He hates Pudding with passion as he is always by Jello's side. In other words, he is awfully jealous of Pudding.
name: Omurice

descr: A naive young girl with pure thoughts. It is as if she just came into this world, she’s excited about everything.
name: Strawberry Daifuku

descr: A soft and cute youngster. He isn't very courageous and can always be found hiding in the shadows. He doesn't like to talk with others and doesn't like it when his feelings get hurt.
name: Salad

descr: An eccentric young man. He is clearly of noble lineage, but chooses to wear bizarre clothing. He constantly discusses parallel universe theory with his friends, and believes that an alternate version of himself must exist in some other continuum. As for his eye patch, everyone is dying to know if it's a deliberate fashion choice, or the result of some battle injury.
name: Caviar

descr: Red Wine is very confident and proud of his strength. He is an expert swordsman. He likes to wear a wide range of extravagant jewelries and clothing. He hates being in places where the sun shines.
name: Red Wine

descr: This young woman exudes an extraordinary charm. She is extremely good at dealing with people and has always been very popular amongst men.
name: Orange Juice

descr: A young guy with a lot of personality. He is an advocate of freedom is a very loyal companion. He adores music; especially rock and rap.
name: Cola

descr: She seems very gentle but can actually be rather mischievous and will often play practical jokes on others.
name: Ume Ochazuke

descr: He doesn't like interacting with others and can be rather harsh when he does. He has absolute confidence in his desserts. He likes to spend his time alone so don't get angry when you get ignored.
name: Pastel de nata

descr: A woman who gives off a very dangerous vibe. It seems as if she is hiding some sort of bitter resentment from the people around her.
name: Seaweed Soup

descr: Cheerful, lively, & somewhat mischievous. She doesn't have a filter and speaks her mind. This has resulted in a lot of people being offended but they all know she means well.
name: Udon

descr: He thinks of himself as a monk but in reality, he is just an ordinary man who likes to be around woman. He doesn't care much for anything that doesn't concern him. The only way to motivate him, is to surround him with beautiful woman.
name: Miso Soup

descr: On the surface, he is arrogant and self-centered but in reality, he is a just fool with a pure heart. He is incapable of handling relationships with people and can often be misunderstood.
name: Yellow Wine

descr: The elder brother of the Tofu twins. He has a tendency to let his thoughts run wild. He may seem gentle and soft but he is actually quite dangerous. He loves rock music and staying up late to do weird things.
name: Sweet Tofu

descr: The younger brother of the Tofu twins. Like his brother, he is also rebellious and strange. Needless to say, the Tofu twins are a rather peculiar pair of brothers.
name: Salty Tofu

descr: A young man who does as he pleases. He doesn't like to be inconvenienced and often sends his wonton spirits to run his errands.
name: Wonton

descr: An optimistic young boy whose great at doing business. He loves food and can always be seen chewing on something. On most days, you can find him roaming around and doing business near the markets.
name: Pancake

descr: There is not a man alive that can resist her calm elegance. She enjoys playing the flute atop a quiet mountain and likes to distant herself from everyone.
name: Cloud Tea

descr: Mature and witty, this lady is very popular among young girls. She enjoys studying history and knows everything there is to know which has allowed her to become a respected historian. She often reminds people not to forget the past and to learn from history.
name: Yuxiang

descr: A Food Soul with a sensitive personality. This makes him seem inherently weak to others, but in actuality he is....?
name: Raindrop Cake

descr: Rice doesn't have any spirit power. Known as an "empty vessel", even talking is hard for her, so she spends her time in Master Attendant's kitchen doing odd jobs. But her obedient, good-natured personality makes her a favorite among all the Food Souls, so everyone looks after her.
name: Rice

descr: Canele always wears a loving smile on her face. She uses her beautiful voice to sing blessings to others. At one point, humanity thought of her as a messenger from God.
name: Canele

descr: She is gentle and melancholic. She seems to be waiting for the right person to bring her happiness. Perhaps a certain Master Attendant may be able to make her happy again.
name: Sweet & Sour Fish

descr: A cat man of little words. He refers to himself as 'we' and treats the cats around him like family. He is extremely forgetful and doesn't care for much except for his cats.
name: Bonito Rice

descr: Toast is full of maturity and has a very high tolerance for others. People feel comfortable and safe around him. Often chased around by sandwich asking to lend him some money. A very reliable person.
name: Toast

descr: Gingerbread may appear small and weak, but her strength far exceeds her stature. For her, guarding objects of importance to her is her sole purpose in life. In order to achieve this goal, she crosses the boundaries between good and evil, using her strong shield to block danger and her sharp sword to cut through obstacles.
name: Gingerbread

descr: A young lady that use to be very popular amongst the people. At one point in time, she was the symbol of harvest and fortune. However, it seems she has lost that symbol now.
name: Laba Congee

descr: A very talkative youngster who likes to go around asking questions. A lot of people are actually quite annoyed by his constant questions.
name: Gyoza

descr: She is confident, aggressive, and likes to challenge the rules. Although she doesn't look very easy to get along with, she is actually a very good person. She believes that she is better suited to 'eradicat misfortunes' than to 'pray for blessings'.
name: Toso

descr: A motivated young girl who is generally very respectful although sometimes she does like to joke around.
name: Pineapple Cake

descr: A cute, albeit confused, little magician. Always carries a egg-shaped magic wand and helps those in need. Very enthusiastic, although sometimes this leads to making bad situations worse,
name: Eggette

descr: A girl who's addicted to Mahjong. Bright and bubbly, every day she looks around for people to join her table. She's empathetic and loyal, so she has many friends, and on a normal day she likes to invite them over for get-togethers. She rarely gets depressed--in her opinion, there's no problem that can't be solved by clicking together a few Mahjong tiles. And she has a lot of those.
name: Sichuan Hotpot

descr: Beer has been alive for nearly 10,000 years. He knows about every event in human history, and has even compiled his knowledge into poems and songs for the sake of transmitting it. However, because he's been alive for too long, everything he says and does is designed to make people laugh. In the end, it's all to keep his own spirits high.
name: Beer

descr: She looks like a cold and careless sister but she’s very meticulous when it comes to caring. Very meticulous and clever minded. Although there is a lot to worry about in her life, she is able to handle everything handed to her.
name: Yunnan Noodles

descr: A girl who enjoys spring time traveling. She often asks Master Attendant to join her and is always thoroughly prepared for her trip. She may seem really clingy but it’s just her caring and gentle personality.
name: Matcha Rice

descr: She claims to be a Food Soul from the Light Kingdom, but the way she looks, talks, and acts are all different from the Light Kingdom's style. She's never opened up to anybody, and people even think she's a little unsociable. But she behaves with incomparable enthusiasm and only gives the cold shoulder to Vodka.
name: Borscht

descr: He hates being touched by people he's not familiar with, and is intensely guarded and adversarial against the outside world. Seems very difficult to get close to.
name: Oyster

descr: Full of energy and constantly happy, this Food Soul wears a smile everyday. He enjoys playing harmless tricks and traveling the world. He lives a carefree life and prefers to avoid conflict when possible. When it comes to Cassata and Cheese, he’s very relaxed and will often be the bud of jokes between the them. He may seem happy on the outside but deep down there’s far more lurking.
name: Pizza

descr: Open minded and kind hearted. This Food Soul likes to socialize and has a massive appetite! She can often teases people but gets away with it because of her beauty and intellect. Her favorite thing to do is tease pizza! When her tricks fail, she can get quite upset. But, just give her some food and she’ll be happy again!
name: Cheese

descr: A girl who likes to travel and document everything she sees in her diary. Likes to examine and discover strange artifacts and incidents and then document it in her personal diary.However, to this date she still hasn't uncovered the secrets behind Miss Black Tea's past. And if she has Miss Milk repeatedly do the same thing, what on earth will happen?
name: Milk Tea

descr: Ddeokbokki's older sister, a traveling artist that loves and excels at dancing. Because she's seen it all in her wanderings across the world, underneath her serene and dignified exterior, she has a gloomy, yet resolute heart. She really cares for Ddeokbokki and supports her in everything she does, but Kimchi also won't hesitate to scold her when she gets up to no good.
name: Kimchi

descr: Kimchi's younger sister, a traveling artist skilled at singing. She seems tenacious, but actually she's got a gentle heart. Her easily-moved personality is the reason why her sister often calls her a "cry baby". She doesn't want her sister to dance to the voice of another singer, so every day she works on her singing, and subconsciously she sees anyone with a good singing voice as her competition.
name: Ddeokbokki

descr: A talented, gorgeous woman who is fearless in battle and ruthless. She looks austere and stiff, but actually she just takes her work seriously and can be also be quite romantic. She has seen action on the battlefield and worked as a guard.
name: Kung Pao Chicken

descr: Pizza’s guardian. He might not seem like the most powerful warrior, but he his strength is not to be questioned. He’s also a jack of all trades, but he hates being bothered.  Prior to meeting Pizza he was quite introverted and preferred observing people from afar. Because of his past, he prefers to keep to himself.
name: Casatta

descr: A Food Soul who stays upbeat all the time and talks with an "earthy" feel. She enjoys growing vegetables and is an arm-wrestling champ. Others see her as a real action-type.
name: Braised Noodles

descr: A mercurial Food Soul who doesn't sweat the small stuff. She's adept at sailing and fighting, and always finds a way to get the things she wants.
name: Rum

descr: A girl with supernatural luck, a bright smile, and a candid personality. She is surprisingly wise, and sometimes reveals poignant insight that seems inconsistent with her appearance. She is interested in medicine, and also reads books on herbal remedies. She always adds herbal medicine to her Recipes--her intent is to improve everybody's health, but it results in the food looking unappetizing.
name: Mung Bean Soup

descr: A haughty Food Soul who never shows his true face or his true feelings to others. But everything he does seems to be in the service of some interest.
name: Green Curry

descr: A Food Soul born in the Light Kingdom who travelled across the broad seas to the South. Over time, he grew to be someone who could withstand harsh environments, possessing a wealth of survival experience.
name: Bak Kut Teh

descr: She has a capricious, temperamental personality and is often accompanied by a butterfly. She has an elegant demeanor befitting her noble-born station in life, but she's also extremely arrogant and haughty. She looks with contempt on all things and will only speak civilly with an Attendant whom she considers a worthy equal. Her hobbies are writing stories and having afternoon tea. To her, there is nothing more important than afternoon tea, and until she's finished it, everything else can wait.
name: Fruit Tart

descr: A lovable Food Soul that lives out in the rural countryside. Loves music and singing, but doesn't have much of an audience due to exceedingly poor musical sensibility.
name: Apple Pie

descr: Always full of spirit, with a swaggering demeanor, and doesn't have any reservations about people based on gender. She's a Food Soul that anybody would want to be friends with.
name: American Corn Bread

descr: A thoroughly sophomoric boy, he always confuses people when he talks, because he rambles and gets off topic. But if forced to make his point, he becomes shy. He's searching everywhere for ways to become stronger, so he can keep up with his Attendant.
name: Fried Chicken

descr: Has a clean, handsome appearance and eyes that see beyond worldly concerns. Through many years of honing, his body and mind have reached a place of extreme strength and transcended the mundane.
name: Butter Tea

descr: Lacks any interest in day-to-day life and has a cold, detached personality. He doesn't like to raise his voice for fear of straining his vocal chords, but he's very self-confident and independent. He loves the opera and will sacrifice everything for it. Though usually calm and restrained, when he's singing opera music, he gives his voice free reign. Due to his excessive love of the opera, he hopes to have a voice capable of playing all kinds of roles.
name: Opera Cake

descr: Seemingly born from the darkness, this petite little figure is often in the arms of a massive bunny doll. Not much of a talker, and mostly only talks with the bunny. He will tentatively talk with others, and will make overly-excited reactions that can be somewhat disconcerting.
name: Durian Pancake

descr: On the surface, he seems to really care about time, but he also turns everything into a complicated mess and starts hesitating and wavering. He has a cowardly, self-abasing personality and thinks of himself as useless, even to the point that he doesn't care about his own existence, which is why he spends all his time with his doll companion. But actually, he also has another personality lurking inside him, both frivolous and egotistical. This side of him has a strong desire for control which stems from his belief that happiness is a fleeting thing, which makes him incredibly greedy for it and drives his love of beautiful objects. These two personalities will swap when his beloved doll falls on the ground or gets dirtied. In reality, whenever his outward self comes under intense provocation, or if he feels like he needs to escape, then his inner personality will emerge.
name: Souffle

descr: A young woman skilled at manipulating her puppet and proud of the fact. She used to work in the palace, so she keeps a high opinion of herself. Aside from her puppet "Lury", she doesn't care for anyone.
name: Dragon's Beard Candy

descr: Has a neutral, gentle personality and always speaks frankly about anything. Holds her ground, to the point of being stubborn. An excellent poet.
name: Osmanthus Cake

descr: Looks like an upstanding, trustworthy Doaist fortune teller. Actually not as reliable as he looks, this guy always enjoys stirring up trouble. But in important matters he becomes reliable, a fellow that people both love and hate.
name: Huangshan Maofeng Tea

descr: Cheerful, straightforward, with a spring in his step. Sometimes he gives people a feeling of unpredictability, but that's not something he dwells on. He's a man of his word, and he despises lies. He has a natural sensitivity to them, and if he senses you've lied, he can become somewhat terrifying.
name: Nagashi Somen

descr: He may be a little introverted, but he likes getting close to people, and can even be a bit clingy. Because he's practically expressionless himself, he also likes to use ceremonial masks and is often carrying them. Every time he feels shy or excited, he'll put one on to cover his face. He enjoys traveling around chronicling all kinds of things, no matter if it's a story of something that truly happened or a tale that someone tells him, he'll write it all down. He believes everything in this world has a reason for being, which is why he's so passionate about seeking these things out.
name: Natto

descr: A genteel lady who likes listening to others talk. She's sensitive to others' feelings, hardworking, and thrifty. She enjoys studying the Five Elements and is always peppering her speech with imaginative turns of phrase.
name: Bibimbap

descr: Lively and cheerful, although a bit impatient. She is shrewd, capable, and skilled at business, but also naturally sharp-tongued. She may be a little prideful and stubborn, but she loves hearing praise from others. At work, she uses her cute appearance to win over her customers.
name: Takoyaki

descr: A gentle person who isn't obstinate, but also doesn't just go along with the crowd. Rather, she maintains a unique personality all her own. Her gentle demeanor is infectious, and the sound of her playing can soothe people's hearts.
name: Doenjang Jjigae

descr: Of noble birth, Parfait is part of society's upper crust, and fame and money don't have any attraction with her. She doesn't care about her standing, only the spirit of freedom. Life must be thrilling to be good. She doesn't like others fawning over her. Perfection is her criterion for doing things, and she has her own standards for how to do things.
name: Parfait

descr: Cappuccino was summoned into existence by a noble couple with no son of their own. He was doted on like a child and given a nobleman's education, growing up in the seminary of the Holy See. From the time he was little, he could hear the voice of god in his dreams, which led him to his love of theology and his decision to get closer to god. He chose to undergo monastic training in the seminary of the Holy See Academy, during which time he got to know Professor Mashed Potatoes, who was there lecturing. He was inspired by Mashed Potatoes' plan to save the world with a seed ark, and so he became an intern at Mashed Potatoes' botanical garden "Garden of Eden".
name: Cappuccino

descr: Seems to have a similar history as Boston Lobster, and his body has been modified by humans. He usually always hides behind Boston Lobster and calls him "Big Brother". Any order that "Big Brother" gives, he'll carry it out without hesitation.
name: Salt 'n Pepper Shrimp

descr: A carefree, undisciplined youth with a perpetual twinkle in his eye. On the surface he's a traveling merchant, but actually he's a con artist. Behind this identity, he secretly researches alchemy and is knowledgeable in both alchemy and medicine. He likes excitement but does not enjoy getting dragged into trouble himself, so he usually finds a way to watch the conflicts he stirs up from the sidelines. He's full of lies and avoids showing his true feelings, but if there's something he's interested in, he'll have a strong desire to get it.
name: Whisky

descr: Double-Ninth Cake is indifferent to the world and doesn't show much emotion, but she's often called upon for help because of her ability to see disasters clearly. She explains how to avoid misfortune, but she herself believes that people should face their own destinies, so she won't solve their problems for them.
name: Double-Ninth Cake

descr: A lazy homebody who won't lift a finger if somebody else can do it for her. She's very curious about the outside world, but she still won't go out to see it for herself. Because of this, she loves reading Milk Tea's travelogues and has become her #1 fan.
name: Pineapple Bun

descr: His seductive smile can capture the hearts of young woman with ease. He may seem kind and warm, but everything he does has ulterior motives, especially when it comes to making woman do as he pleases.  He loves the scent of blood and lacks the familiarity of warmth. Some say his body is cold as ice.
name: Bloody Mary

descr:
A fashionista who doesn’t mind having the eyes of others on her, she always does things her way. She may seem like she lacks manners, but really she’s just not a stickler for formalities. She’s a little bad at reading the atmosphere and is a straight-talker.
Whenever she runs into Oden, she always finds things to nit-pick about.
name: Okonomiyaki

descr: Looks solemn and chilly on the outside, but inside she's a total girly-girl. She believes that the existence of Food Souls on Tierra is a blessing to humanity, and she wants to spread goodness and love throughout the world. As a soldier, she holds herself to strict standards.
name: Donut

descr: A girl who loves outdoor adventures and can survive easily in jungles or river country. Likes hoarding survival supplies.
name: Mandarin Squirrel Fish

descr: Looks like a total "grass-eater" little gentleman. A ladykiller who is romantic and extremely warm and friendly to everyone. But also naturally a little naughty. Easily tempts others.
name: Eggnog

descr: Devote your faith to justice. Have good will in your heart and actions. Wipe all evil away into the darkness.
name: Pretzel

descr: The head of Reverie Valley in the Light Kingdom, she may seem detached from mortal affairs and aloof to the concerns of people, but in actuality she just doesn’t understand the ways of the world due to never having been a part of it. Bird's Nest Soup doesn’t like flame and is somewhat repulsed by humans, thinking them to be overly-covetous, but in major matters of right and wrong, she’ll still lend a helping hand.
name: Bird's Nest Soup

descr: Really wants to become a powerful and reliable ruler, but clearly still a guy who hasn't grown up yet. His penchant for flaunting his abilities often leads Eggnog to want to bully him. Craves recognition.
name: Turkey

descr: A saint who already listens to the wishes of others and treats everyone with equal goodwill. When needed, she can fearlessly drive away evil creatures.
name: Fondant Cake

descr: A gentle and warm young man who is empathetic to even the slightest of emotions. He runs an eatery making only the most authentic Sakurajima oden. His shop and the oden he makes has the power to soothe people's hearts, attracting customers from all over. Even if it's an old wino in the middle of the night, Oden will listen patiently to all their troubles great and small, and offer sympathetic advice.
name: Oden

descr: A general who has never tasted defeat and very proud of his status. If someone crosses him, he gets angry. He's crowned himself king after a long period of only knowing victory.
name: Champagne

descr: Known as the "little mister sunshine", Lion's Head is as lively as a lion, infecting everyone around him with his cheerfulness. As a craftsman, his bold vision and attention to detail allow him to make marvelous lanterns.
name: Lion's Head

descr:
A lively and animated girl who loves excitement, her strong emotions always infect the people around her. She hates feeling hot and stuffy, but also loves all kinds of summer activities, so she's developed the habit of always having an ice-cold drink on her.
She has a good relationship with Candy Apple.
name: Ramune

descr: A fox spirit living in a shrine who calls himself a divine emissary. After the shrine fell into disrepair, he found that solitary lifestyle too quiet and took to visiting nearby villages and messing with the humans, frequently shifting into different forms to play tricks on them.
name: Inarizushi

descr: Food, fortune, or fame-- as long as it's within his grasp, he wants it. That's why he always seems in a hurry. In reality, he's very generous to his friends, even though he seems like he doesn't care for Master Attendant.
name: Buddha's Temptation

descr: Formerly known as "the Hegemon-King". He is easy-going and frank, and not the type to carry a grudge against those who harmed him, only against those who harmed his friends. He would never allow anyone to bully his friends. He is formidable, but not the most formidable intellect. He puts a lot of trust in his friends.
name: Dragon & Phoenix

descr: A Food Soul slumbering at the bottom of a lake in an abundant tea-producing region of the Light Kingdom. He is indifferent to pretty much everything, and people mistake him for a dragon god, beings also known to slumber at lake bottoms. He enjoys cool, brisk climates and does not like being disturbed by noisy people. However, according to a Food Soul who wished to remain anonymous, he's really just an "otaku" who loves sleeping in and isn't good at socializing.
name: Longjing Tea

descr: She has an extreme sense of justice and will always step forward to right wrongs. She's also very enthusiastic and hospitable, and can be straightforward but always polite. She is a totally reliable lady.
name: Mapo Tofu

descr: A tenacious Food Soul full of vitality. He's always raring to go and energizes those around him. But because he often does things not by the book, he's seen as dishonest and underhanded.
name: Unadon

descr: A disciplined young man who holds rituals and appearances to be very important. As a result, he is very respectful, modest, and proper in his actions and treats others with warmth.
name: Tteokguk

descr: An aloof-seeming, but actually quite ardent boy. He doesn't have a way with words, and he's used to using actions to express concerns he has for others' health. He's always saying the words, "I'm here."
name: Soba

descr: A young man born in flame. The pain he experienced at the hands of flame led to his decision to take up the path of the warrior. He must be ever-vigilant to save as many people as he can!
name: Yakitori

descr: Righteous and passionate. This noodle shop owner seems to want to spend the years quietly, but underneath her warm and gentle facade, a decidedly different past is hidden.
name: Tonkotsu Ramen

descr: He is not very wise in the ways of the world, and so seems a little standoffish. He doesn't like coming into contact with too many people. He once upon a time committed many acts of harm against others, although unwittingly, but he will work hard to help those he wants to help.
name: Realgar Wine

descr: This noble born woman is naturally proud, and although she has a lively personality, her self-restraint makes it hard to let go and do what she wants to do.
name: Osechi

descr: Even in a world of chaos, he maintains his integrity and pursues his goals wholeheartedly without seeking power or profit. He stays true to himself and strives to live with a clean conscience. When pushed to the breaking point, he can show a persistence that others have never seen before.
name: Zitui Bun

descr: A siren with an extreme desire to be loved. She wears a fish-tail dress, but all who see her true face run away panic-stricken. All she can do in her grave disappointment is bury them and await the next being that might love her.
name: Surströmming

descr: An alluring, silent beauty who isn't good at expressing emotions and never has much to say. However, she's got a sensitive heart and favors briskly cold places. Although she often writes runes that others can't decipher, she is also proficient in regular writing and loves recording all she sees in her travels.
name: Snowskin Mooncake

descr: A seemingly gentle girl whose never truly seen this world with her own eyes. Because of her well-heeled upbringing, she has no concept of money and has no idea how cruel some things she does are. She seeks the highest quality in all things, and nothing that she eats, wears, or uses isn't of the utmost luxury.
name: Stargazy Pie

descr: Full of curiosity for everything. Wants to disassemble, take apart, and explore the essence of everything he can get his hands one and restore them to their simplest and purest forms.
name: Waffle

descr: A man who enjoys drinking alcohol and is always wearing oiran attire. He looks a little coquettish, and knows how to create a warm atmosphere and butter people up, but really that’s his way of distancing himself from others. He doesn’t trust others, but for those that are straightforward and even seem a little silly, even if they annoy him, he rarely shows it.
name: Junmai Daiginjo

descr: An opportunist with a talent for business-- and not an ounce of talent for writing poetry. To this day, he's not written one "waka" poem that's gotten any praise.
name: Matsutake Dobinmushi

descr: She has no scruples when it comes to people she admires, and she is willing to indulge anything they wish to do. She'd even help an object of her devotion to cover up their crimes.
name: Black Pudding

descr: She's very enthusiastic and likes making dolls that look just like her for people she likes. However, she has to use that person's hair to make the doll's hair-- whether they consent or not-- because only then will the doll be effective in warding away evil. She doesn't believe in exchanging goods for money, but rather in a sincere exchange of a gift for a gift. She'll occasionally use a doll to tease others, and when the hurt that she sustains takes too much of a psychological toll, she can't help but let it flow out. That's why she has likes running water, because she thinks it fends off disasters.
name: Hishi Mochi

descr: If her suggestions are shot down, she isn’t bold enough to assert herself further. Even if she doesn’t really like what someone else said, she won’t take issue with it. But Candy Cane is trying hard to grow.
name: Candy Cane

descr: She usually just seems like an innocent little girl who gives people a feeling of childlike simplicity. She's not shy around strangers at all and likes inviting people to play in her "Candy House" which she made from marshmallows. She hates hot temperatures and fire. When around flames, her personality will change.
name: Marshmallow

descr: In his former life, Gyudon was a rigidly traditional samurai on Sakurajima, but after one particular conflict, he started to examine his thoughts and learned to accept novelty, and his personality became more cheery and outgoing as well. He is trying to incorporate the ideas of foreign cultures into his own way of thinking in a peaceful way.
name: Gyudon

descr: White Truffle has prodigious literary attainments and poetic talents, but those things only show through in the works that she pens secretly. To other people, their first impression of her is that of a particularly brilliant technologist, and not the romance found in her writings.
name: White Truffle

descr: A diligent young woman who is always very forthcoming in taking on chores and who enjoys talking with visitors from all over. She learned some pharmacology from Calamus Wine and likes making desserts, so she often makes herself some pastries and tea to relax with.
name: Almond Tofu

descr: A forgotten god who is merciful to humans. If you make a request to his face, he will do all he can to help, but due to certain matters, he is unwilling to return to the world.
name: Wuyi Da Hong Pao

descr: An inspector for the Food Soul law enforcement agency Eye of Horus. Carrying the Code in his left hand and a musket rifle in his right, for now he follows around Sachertorte as they carry out missions. Although he often has a smile on his face, he’s actually more obstinate and tight-lipped than cold and aloof Sachertorte. Because of past experience, he has vowed to bring justice to all the wrongs in the world. He’s a young man who is striving for growth.
name: Baguette

descr: First violinist of the travelling Fantasy Opera Troupe. A master of melody who loves all things natural and considers children to be the purest blessings from the gods. He's an admirer of his fellow troupe member Opera Cake and Opera Cake's gifted singing, but his favorite person is still the troupe's leader. He follows his heart, and if there's something he likes, he'll put in the time and come up with a way to turn it into an object he can collect-- for instance, writing down his favorite moods and emotions as melodies. However, this example in particular is the most socially acceptable of his collecting habits.
name: Blue Cheese

descr: A proud being that has somewhat fallen due to a past in which he was betrayed by a "god". The originally white-feathered wings behind him have become black wings of bone. He looks down with contempt on all and will not set aside his pride. After falling, he let go of a previous insistence on etiquette and formalities. Now he does as he pleases with reckless abandon.
name: Lamb Chops

descr: Black Truffle is always used to toying with the emotions of others, especially in front of an audience. To her, adoration is the sweetest of delicacies. Her glamorous appearance makes it almost impossible for people to resist wanting to get near her, but at the same time her capricious personality and evil features make people want to steer clear. Black Truffle’s real favorite thing to do is to bully White Truffle. Seeing White Truffle’s face turn red with exasperation leaves her feeling all warm inside.
name: Black Truffle

descr: Tequila loves to go adventuring everywhere and to hunt down Fallen Angels. He has a cheery disposition, although he can get fairly intense when he makes a mistake. He joined the Holy See because of an old friend, and he works hard so that others won't meet with tragedy the way his partner did. He has an exceptionally noble demeanor.
name: Tequila

descr: He wants to become a samurai, and that's why he's always carrying a Tanto knife and wearing armor. He also loves carp. He has a romantic streak, always fantasizing that he's a justice-dealing samurai, and that all his experiences in the world will become legendary tales.
name: Kashiwa Mochi

descr: Soft Serve Cone is an icy-cool young woman with a touch of sweetness to her. She loves a life of novelty and imagination, and she's at her best when she's trying anything new, whereas she does not enjoy conservative and stubborn people and things. She's very frank in expressing her likes and dislikes, as she does not like wasting time beating around the bush. Her powerfully frosty nature helps her always keep her cool, so she's very level-headed. She almost never loses it, except when she's around Master Attendant, which will cause her heart to melt uncontrollably. Then she won't be able to contain her sweet, girlish side.
name: Soft Serve Cone

descr: His main occupation is botanist, with a side job as a university professor, rated by his students as the most popular teacher in all of Tierra. He's a handsome man with a "Mori-style" woodland aesthetic. He has a fresh and tender appearance, a pure innocence, and the heart of a child willing to embrace the whole world.
name: Mashed Potatoes

descr: A lively and charming young woman with a strong curiosity for the unknown and an unusual obsession with her personal "god"-- absolutely not allowing any person to infringe upon or defile him. To matters of the outside world, she's fairly clueless and has a habit of attaching herself to the first person she sees, like a baby duckling imprinting on its mama. If it's a person she trusts, she'll believe anything they say.
name: Margarita

descr: Easter Egg often hides in his shell because he's introverted, but he's very persistent when it comes to his areas of expertise. As a machinist, Easter Egg spends his days calibrating and repairing weapons for others, and he even makes mechs that run on Magic Crystals or Soul Power. He's not a powerful fighter himself, but his mechs have extreme combat ability.
name: Easter Egg

descr: Appears gentle like water, but actually has a firm will. Ambitious yet overly idealistic, with a bit of impulsiveness and stubbornness. After experiencing sacrifices, becomes more stable and realistic, but still retains some stubbornness. Once a belief is established, it is carried through to the end.
name: Wuchang Fish

descr: The picture of genteel refinement, this young girl abounds with enthusiasm. However, because she's worried her enthusiasm will put people off, she usually phrases her thoughts as probing questions when she speaks.
name: Umeshu

descr: Not long after Minestrone was summoned, he was sold by his Attendant to an underground organization to be a test subject. After escaping after many years, he was transformed into a monster that feeds off negative emotions. He is constantly on the run, and vengeance consumes his heart. He has a strong survival instinct, and even though he survives off of nightmares every day, he still won't lay down and die as others might wish. Although his body and mind are constantly mired in pain, he always forces himself to wear a smile on his face and never show pain or weakness in front of others. However, he has no idea how stiff and twisted his smile can appear.
name: Minestrone

descr: A kind and personable doctor who knows how to amuse people. He has exceptional medical skills and a strong sense of responsibility, and will diligently put in work behind-the-scenes for others. Outside of work, he’s also very considerate and will frequently tease Pretzel and act as a mediator between Pretzel and others. With Black Pudding he may get into disagreements and spats over differences of opinion over medical issues.
name: Muenchner Weisswurst

descr:
Pad Thai is a clever, bold, and strong woman whose independent spirit has helped her stand out in the ruthless world of business. She is also a believer in the Buddha by birth.
Being calm under fire, seeing things from a unique angle, and not backing down to authority are her hallmarks. She is a real-deal superwoman.
name: Pad Thai

descr: A refined and genial youth who always seems to be thinking of others. He claims to have no real combat ability, but the smile on his face gives people the feeling that there’s more than meets the eye.
name: Tsukimi Dango

descr: Seen as the source of disasters and misunderstood by people, with all of her actions distorted and misinterpreted. After "seeing clearly" the true nature of men, she cared even less about the opinions of others and pressed all of her advantages to get more for herself with wanton disregard. After making the acquaintance of the nobles, she rapidly became a belle of the ball, pursued by all of the noblemen. She flaunted her beauty and purposefully enticed nobles from all corners into a scramble over her, bringing about political ruin and thus becoming known as a witch.
name: Madeleine

descr: Turducken is a funeral director who owns a funeral hall named "Nirvana". With a smile on her face, she beautifies the bodies of the dead and then, humming a happy song, sends them off to be cremated or buried. In her eyes, death is the first step in a new life, and so she gives the dead her sincere blessings. However, due to her tall stature and because she's often seen wandering around graveyards dressed all in black, many people think she is an extremely dangerous Food Soul.
name: Turducken

descr: Born in a war-ridden age, she spent her early years as a mercenary active in Gloriville, Nevras, and other locales. Later, due to a chance occurrence, she gave up taking part in human civil wars and turned her sights on Fallen Angels.
name: Hardtack

descr: Youthful looking, but mature on the inside. If there’s something she believes in firmly, she throws herself into it with all her strength. She values the the honor of martial arts, and doesn’t believe martial arts is for street fighting or showing off one’s power, so if she’s asked to demonstrate her skills, she can get angry.
name: Double Skin Milk

descr: A robot-like and coldly-calculating archangel. It seems the only thing left in his life is the Holy See. He works to the utmost to preserve the light in this world, but all anyone can see is the reserved and refined side of him. He believes strongly in the goodness of the world and grieves for his former comrades that have fallen into darkness. Even so, Croissant still punishes his enemies with cold ruthlessness. Croissant doesn't care if he's misunderstood by others, and his methods may be a bit harsh, but they are always the best course of action after serious consideration.
name: Croissant

descr: Through his own hard work, diligence, and the help of kind friends, Fish and Chips has embarked on the path of the Knights Templar. He has faith that through his efforts, he can save the world and convert those fallen creatures to the light.
name: Fish and Chips

descr: Mango Pomelo Sago also goes by another name, "Sweet Dew of the Willow Branch". She believes strongly in herself, has a natural appreciation for beauty and art, and has always forged her own path in terms of fashion and aesthetics. When she was born, she wasn't a powerful Food Soul at all, but her Attendant told her again and again: "You are the most beautiful. You are the best," and also gave her the name Sweet Dew of the Willow Branch, which implies that she is like a lucky star bestowed by the gods upon the world. These thoughts sunk in over time, and Mango Pomelo Sago became a confident and big-hearted artist. She's active in several fields of art and boldly explores the creativity of the world, firm in her belief that in her own way, she can make the world a more beautiful place.
name: Mango Pomelo Sago

descr: A wanton and reckless young man. He hasn't a care for what others think, and is skilled at scoffing at others who to take kindly to him. But as far as he's concerned, perhaps the only thing he truly cares about is his little sister. The guilt he feels over his sister has morphed into a powerful protective urge. Because his body is slowly turning into wood, the gradual loss of sensation accompanying that has made him exceedingly infatuated with any extreme feeling, be it pain or cold or heat. Although he quite likes the icy cold that Century Egg produces, he's not willing to admit it.
name: Cordyceps

descr: A young nobleman who is strict with himself but lenient with others. He is proper without being pedantic and tactful without being a stickler for etiquette. Although he holds a position of nobility, he conducts affairs in a low-key manner and doesn't take advantage of his authority and Food Soul powers to run roughshod over others. Instead, he skillfully makes use of his position and abilities, and has joined the Food Soul law enforcement agency "Eye of Horus", protecting and escorting the people of Midgar and surrounding areas, and maintaining social stability.
name: Sachertorte

descr: An easy-going and free-wheeling woman with a strong, independent will with no regard for bureaucratic rules and regulations. She is a strong swordfighter with impressive accomplishments who is used to fighting alone.
name: Chrysanthemum Wine

descr: Full of wiles, a consummate performer, and a woman both resourceful and decisive who excels at moving from strength to strength. Her powerful cunning and scheming have secured for her a position in the Holy Church.
name: Chicken Strip Soup

descr: She's a creature of habit who lives almost entirely in her own world. As far as Cookie's concerned, nothing is more full of charm than a plan old clump of molding clay, and nothing gives her joy more than giving it a soul.
name: Cookie

descr: A youth with the heart of a warrior born with "ghost eyes" that grant him the ability to see ghosts. He believes the meaning of his existence is to beat back ghost hordes, slay wicked forces, and uphold the good. The copper blade he holds shatters easily, but it can be repaired by slaying ghosts.
name: Laba Noodles

descr: A brazen and vixenish young woman who brandishes a great axe which seems out of place with her appearance. She possesses shocking combat ability. She's very straightforward with expressing her likes, and against enemies she has a vicious streak which you won't find in ordinary girls. Her body is in the process of lignifying, resulting in loss of various sensations such as tiredness, pain, taste, and smell.
name: Chishui Moth Tea

descr: When the world was destroyed, Rice received a concentrated blast of the Power of Dreams, turning her into an emissary of the God of Beginnings and recreating the world. Even though Rice is a god, to herself, she’s still her Master’s Food Soul.
name: Rice SP

descr: After Boston Lobster escaped from a laboratory, he came to The Light Kingdom. And then while developing his powers in The Light Kingdom, he received the help of a mystery person.
name: Boston Lobster SP

descr: She has a rich variety of emotions and facial expressions, and usually she laughs and giggles cordially with everyone, but she can always reason things through right away and make the optimal decision. Sometimes she may even seem cold and cruel in her decision making. In a group, she is the strategist and guide, often making reasonable, yet difficult to swallow decisions. But every time, she reproaches herself for this and dislikes this trait of hers.
name: Kakigori

descr: A warlike and thrill-seeking youth. He is fiercely loyal to his own desires, acts according to his own ideas, and doesn’t care about how others perceive him. He lives by his own set of rules and is obsessive-compulsive about his life habits, particularly about the order and timing of how things are done.
name: Jinhua Ham

descr: He never cared at all for the role of Pope, nor did he want to become Pope, but his constant evading caused a disaster to brew. He is a bit more reflective than before, but still retains his warm temperament.
name: Beer SP

descr: A genteel and intelligent woman of strong character, with the highest attainments in music, chess, literature, and painting. Although lacking in fortune and social standing, she’s always good to those around her. After fortuitously becoming the proprietor of Ink Pavilion, she poured herself into the work and turned it into a famous tea house. Aside from generally being a place of elegant pursuits such as appreciating tea and music, the pavilion’s staff often go about righting wrongs and upholding justice, garnering no shortage of praise and attracting quite a few scholars and gentlemen to its tables.
name: Dongtang

descr: She’s a street kid who hangs around the avenues and alleys. She used to be in a band, but she left because she found dealing with interpersonal drama a nuisance. She’s casual and undisciplined and enjoys soaking in hot springs. When she plays the drums, she hides her emotions by putting a paper bag on her head.
name: Instant Noodles

descr: Junmai Daiginjo's faithful hound, so loyal that if Daiginjo told him to go die, he would happily slit his own throat. He knows some things aren't ideal, but he'll still do as Daiginjo says. Although he's a little fed up with some of Daiginjo's actions, he still goes along with him and somewhat pampers him. He is called a merman because the accessories on his body are like fish scales and allow him to "swim" around in the air and up walls even though he's on land. It's also how he sneaks up on targets and hides himself.
name: Mackerel Ichiyaboshi

descr: The royal lantern Longxi Cured Ham carries can project the most important scenes from a dead creature's life. As an inheritor of the mystical art of corpse-walking, legend has it that she can control the abilities of those terrifying creatures of the grave. As chance would have it, she joined the "Nether World", and she seeks the traces of one particular corpse via various burial objects and ancient corpse "memories". Longxi Cured Ham enjoys researching the stories contained in ancient corpses, and she hates garlic, sunlight, and flame. As to why, she won't tell, and other don't dare ask.
name: Longxi Cured Ham

descr: The leader of Venerable Moon. He looks fierce, but he actually has the temperament of a child. He has a harsh view of humanity, but when one really needs help, after giving the person a tongue-lashing, he'll pull him or her behind him and protect them. He places great importance on loyalty. When feeling shy, the fish roe bomb by his side will explode.
name: Mentaiko

descr: He used to abstain from killing, but later caused the deaths of some people. After his own master passed, he made a decision to roam the land. In the end, Wensi Tofu had an epiphany: possessing this power was actually the will of the gods. As the Buddha said, if I don’t enter hell, who will? If I do enter hell, then others no longer need to.
name: Wensi Tofu

descr: Bingfen is a teacher to all, responsible for coordinating all kinds of duties for the whole of the Capital and the owner of Darcy, who can tame any "lunatic". People swallowed by Darcy will be forcefully calmed down by its juice and begin to regret the things they have done, and even start to blubber and sob, reducing them to a state that they would rather not remember. However, Bingfen can inspect the emotions of the swallowed people and soothe them. Darcy's birth was initially to compensate for Bingfen's loss of the sense of taste, but later it was discovered its juice can calm people in order to undergo healing.
name: Bingfen

descr: Although not a true elf, he's every bit as arrogant as one and is recognized as a noble by all elven peoples. His passionate-looking exterior belies a particularly pure and innocent personality.
name: Martini

descr: His former master was a reincarnation of Xuan Wu, one of the four gods of the Light Kingdom and the first person to bring the kingdom under a single rule. Xuan Wu was a fierce and ambitious person whose sole confidant was Century Egg, and upon Xuan Wu’s death, without Century Egg’s consent, Xuan Wu ordered that Century Egg be walled up in the tomb with him, so that Century Egg would always be by his side. Because Food Souls are immortal, Century Egg was trapped in this darkness for hundreds of years, during which time his entire mind collapsed in despair. After being accidentally saved by Cordyceps and Chishui Moth Tea, he finally saw a ray of light. His long period of confinement left him ignorant of the world, only able to robotically heed the instructions of this light (Cordyceps). He saw him as the light of his soul.
name: Century Egg

descr: A long-haired youth who wears old-fashioned armor. He looks cold and reserved, and the muscles all over his body are always rippling with tension, like a pointy tip ready to pierce an enemy's heart at will. He was born with an innate sense of loyalty and dignity. If he considers you his master, then he will give everything to the brink of death to protect your spot on the throne. He will not abide any betrayal. On the surface, you're his master, but in reality these "master-servant contracts" are inevitably a two-way street. While he is protecting you, you also must endure his paranoia and possessiveness.
name: Royal Jelly

descr: An iron-willed general who puts the good of the nation above all else. All acts of enjoyment are a waste to him. He has a pleasing appearance, but he always looks cold and aloof. He doesn't look very threatening, but when he gets angry, he becomes quite dangerous. Usually he doesn't deign to trifle with those who look down on him, but over time, he establishes a reputation for himself.
name: Beef Wellington

descr:
She is a virgo and a perfectionist who works as a restorer of cultural relics. She loves restoring antiques, and her most impressive skill is restoring antique clocks. In her pursuit of precision, she shows great patience and focus during her work, and even appears a bit stern. There's no ancient clock she can't fix, no matter how complex, and the more difficult the restoration job is, the more excited she gets. She often grinds away for months or even years, and doesn't stop until the clock is finally running like new again.
She believes ancient craftsmanship holds an immense amount of artistry and wisdom, and she adores and praises their handiwork.
name: Ginger Milk Pudding

descr:
He never goes and does something on his own accord, and even if it is something that he really can't avoid, he still won't put all his effort into it. He's always emphasizing how weak and helpless he is. If a difference arises between him and someone else, he'll immediately give in, and if it comes to a struggle, he'll run away.
His catch phrase is "Whatever (floats your boat!)".
name: Mixed Fish Soup

descr: A Food Soul who stands in a neutral ground between humans and Food Souls and attaches great importance to the rules. Due to the passing of an old friend, he now runs a detective agency. His great love of Sakurajima leads him to hope for its continued stability. He is often teased by others because of his diminutive stature.
name: Matcha

descr: A young man who gets easily riled up and has a dazzling smile. He carries around an ammo clip and raises a ferret named Snowball. To attack, he loads thunder bullets into the weapon strapped to his arm. He has no control over the blood in his body, and when he gets hot, he'll go out of control attacking others. He always has cuts and scrapes on his body.
name: Spicy Duck Blood Soup

descr: Grass Jelly seems like a gentle, soft-spoken, and harmless young lady. Dressed in oriental attire with a twist of modern fashion, she is always sunny-eyed and cheerful. Grass Jelly is a fan and collector of all types of games—and she even creates her own. Her exact age is unknown, but she was once the Food Soul of an immortal who lived atop a mystical mountain. She has the ability to manipulate space itself, and after leaving the mountaintop, she began using this ability to create her own gamified micro-dimensions, where she makes the rules. She likes to reward the winners and punish the losers, and according to legend, whoever wins her games will receive a gift from the ancient immortal.
name: Grass Jelly

descr: Chewing Gum was summoned into being in the fires of war, but does not wish to become a soldier who simply follows orders all the time. He is by nature a freedom-seeker, unwilling to become anyone's property. He rebelled, but was unable to remove the shackles of his oath to his attendant. The shackles dig into his wrists and ankles, overtime becoming a part of the eternal pain he feels, yet he remains undaunted. He has a quirky personality, and he's willing to make friends on his path to freedom, but no one can truly make him halt his steps.
name: Chewing Gum

descr: A youngster with fantastic swimming ability. He's dexterous, diligent, and excels at various odd jobs aboard a ship. Since joining the Peaceful Merchant Hall, he's become universally praised for his work ethic and the constant care he shows for others.
name: Jianbing Guozi

descr: Formerly the king of a certain small island in Sakurajima. He's a self-styled man of the people and enjoys getting together with friends around a campfire, drinking and telling tall tales. He is quiet territorial, but also patient (it takes three years or more to make aged awamori, or "kusu"). He enjoys the company of beautiful women, as well as the well-muscled bodies of his own gender. He believes there are too many beautiful things in this world, and in order to protect them, he feels it's a necessity to get rid of the unseemly things in life, like exiling a foreign enemy.
name: Awamori

descr: Nanjing Roast Duck hails from the Evil Capital, and what she witnessed there formed her scheming, suspicious personality. She always wears a gentle smile, but that smile is also an unfathomable abyss. She excels at disguising herself as a harmless innocent, while in fact she’s always weighing how things will play to her benefit. She’ll think of ways to get other people to do things, but because of her gentle demeanor, they often don’t even realize they’re being used. She’s accompanied by four little white ducks, and although they’re a handful, they’re the creatures she trusts most of all.
name: Nanjing Roast Duck

descr: Mousse was once the most famous Food Soul in his country, outstanding in brains, brawn, and looks. But because he was inculcated by his Attendant with an obsession to "become the most perfect Food Soul in order to be worthy of his Attendant's efforts to cultivate him", he never was truly free to make his own life choices. His life continued like this until an unimaginable murder attempt befell him, and he was gravely injured. Thankfully, a few of Mousse's good friends that he treated sincerely in his normal life were there to save him and bring him back to life. From then on, excessive spirit power loss caused irreversible harm, and his appearance changed into that of an 8-year-old boy. His memories of his life before was hazy, although afterward under the care of his friends, he gradually recovered scraps of it. Mousse is currently the leader of the Fantasy Opera Troupe.
name: Mousse

descr: The fact that he looks and sounds like a little kid really gets to him, and he gives people the impression that he’s pretending to be a grown-up. He has a vicious tongue. If he sees something not to his liking, or someone treats him like a little child, he will just not let it go. He has a pretty straightforward personality, but he’s a little shy about expressing his true feelings.
name: Fried Tofu Puff

descr: A very cool, collected person who always gives people a sense that there's more than enough. He observes his opponent's movements from the shadows, never taking any challenge too lightly. To his master, he's mostly quite loyal, but if he feels the attendant isn't worthy of respect, he will sever the relationship, without giving the attendant a chance to speak. Although he's getting on in years, he still looks forward to growing as a person.
name: Yuba Vegetable Spring Roll

descr: Paella is the lead actor of the Fantasy Opera Troupe. Her extreme ambition and bold performing style has attracted countless admirers. She's naturally uninhibited and open-hearted, doesn't live life according to the rules, and is willing to throw all caution to the wind to protect someone she believes in. In her eyes, respect should be mutual, or else she's definitely going to take an eye for an eye.
name: Paella

descr: When eating something, he feels at peace in his heart, and so is fairly tranquil. But when his mouth is empty, he goes into "rage mode" and starts rampaging. Anzu Ame built a little house in Nevras's Polar Snowfield, and normally lives there. Whenever an adventurer, or even the king of a nation, comes to the Polar Snowfield in search of the fabled fantasy apricot "rainbow candy", Anzu Ame and Braised Beancurd Skin will act as their guide.
name: Anzu Ame

descr: A girl with a bubbly personality and an active mind. She enjoys encountering new things, and her curiosity knows no bounds. She is always brimming with self-confidence, and so also has a strong desire to win. She used to roam all around Gloriville and has a store of knowledge about the region. She is an ace detective for the Sunset Agency.
name: Candy Apple

descr: Upbeat, cheery, and burningly enthusiastic, although he usually just likes goofing off all over the place, when he gets down to business, he's quite reliable. Because he sees himself as a leader, he often looks after others, but sometimes he can be ridiculously cute himself, and even has the ability to attract small animals. He's great to get along with and knows how to liven up a room. He studies the ancient and slowly-disappearing art of demon exorcism with his master, and he's constantly striving to improve himself in order to uphold justice and protect those around him.
name: Fire Crystal Persimmon Cake

descr: She's a non-confrontational, good-hearted girl who knows how to make her own decisions and think for herself. Sweet Lotus Seed Soup's zither playing on the one hand has a soporific effect, and on the other can promote healing. Because of the countless people she harmed while with the Heretics, she hopes to bring help to even more people now.
name: Sweet Lotus Seed Soup

descr: 为人通透，不易为外界动摇。拥有冷静而准确的判断力，待同伴温柔体贴，拥有慈爱之心。然而，在不认可对方为伙伴时，态度就会激烈转变。对同伴以外的任何人都非常冷淡。
name: 烧汁豆腐衣

descr: He has a smooth personality and an ever-present smile on his face that makes people feel he's being polite, but also heartfelt. There is an air of arrogance to his elegant and unhurried demeanor, but he can also be unpredictable when you get close. The mirror he holds can tell if anything is genuine or fake, and it can also create virtual illusions. As both the Antiquities Appraiser and Vice Curator of Nanli Print Shop, he has duties both big and small that put him in many different situations and in contact with all kinds of people.
name: Mingsixi

descr: He looks extremely withdrawn and taciturn on the surface, but actually he's just not good at conversing with others because he isn't familiar with the ways of the world. He also has a pure, sincere side. Because of his past experiences, he doesn't trust humans and is always on high-alert around them. Beyond that, he loves animals and has personally taken care of many of them. He can even talk to them.
name: Lamb Spine Hotpot

descr: With both good and evil sides and a temperament as changeable as the weather, when she's in a good mood she will extend a helping hand to humans; but when her mood is bad, she'd just as soon slaughter them. She seems addicted to fun, but really it's just that she has seen through the boring facade of the world.
name: Ubagai

descr: A young man as refined and composed as always, but with a decided Machiavellian streak. He once infiltrated the Holy Church as a spy to uncover some unknown secrets of the past buried in the darkness.
name: Peking Duck SP

descr: He always stays quietly on Baqi Island, doing origami by himself. He is both the ferryman and the guardian of the island. He believes that people carrying sin with them should not be allowed onto Baqi Island, and the only way on is via his nori seaweed paper boat.
name: Nori

descr: Junshan Silver Needle Tea is a warrioress adventuring in the world. After meeting Royal Jelly in Reverie Valley and being defeated by him, she admired his skill and decided to stay, swearing an oath to defeat him one day. While in Reverie Valley, aside from challenging her rival, she helps clear out Fallen Angel.
name: Junshan Silver Needle

descr: Formerly bound by shrine clerics using a special spell matrix, he was trapped in Chaos for a long time, until Inarizushi discovered him and freed him from his hellish prison. He has an affection for Inarizushi like a fledgling chick has for its mother. In front of Inarizushi, he will appear to be obedient and innocent, but before others he gets downright menacing.
name: Kitsune Udon

descr: Because he often can't remember events of the past, he easily flies into a rage and is unwilling to trust anyone. As the head of the Holy Church, he has been granted some tasks that he must accomplish, and he can appear extraordinarily wicked. His personality has been cultivated into one of fragility and unbridled stubbornness due to the incessant demands placed on him by the members of the church.
name: Hibiscus Tea

descr: Five Snake Soup is a Food Soul summoned by Hibiscus Tea, and he listens to no one aside from Hibiscus Tea. Because being near him relieves Hibiscus Tea's pain, whenever the time comes, he will obediently curl himself up around Hibiscus Tea. He has an instinctive love and possessiveness of the person who summoned him, and no matter who that person is, he will be absolutely loyal to him or her. Aside from the one who summoned him, no one else even appears in his world.
name: Five Snake Soup

descr: Tanuki Soba is a crafty merchant who works for the Nine Tails organization in charge of managing daily expenses and community outreach.
name: Tanuki Soba

descr: With her ethereal and fine singing voice, she works hard as a choir member to spread joy and happiness and hopes to pass on her praise of the Lord to more people. She likes to practice her singing by herself, and sometimes she even writes her own songs. She has the personality of a little angel, but in reality she also has a tiny devilish streak too.
name: Bagel

descr: Lutefisk is one of the seven teachers of the Food Soul organization "The School", in charge of pharmaceutics. He is somewhere between genius and madness, and whether he does good or evil is totally up to the guidance of his peers. When his emotions run high, he will unconsciously give off a corrosive liquid all around him, for which he has been excluded and rejected before. He has intense inferiority and anxiety issues, and he believes that the only things that don't hate him are dead things. Champagne arranged an independent laboratory for him in The School, and the specimens soaking in there are all his "students" whom he gives daily lectures to.
name: Lutefisk

descr:
Goose Barnacle loves to fight and loves to win. He's terribly self-conceited and lords over the entire underground world under the title "Gate of Hell". He has the arrogance to think he's second to none, and the ability to back it up. He is straightforward and by-the-book, and would never allow anyone to violate the "rules of the game" in his territory. On the notorious "Black Street" he has the utmost prestige.
Although he looks menacing and nefarious on the outside, and although no one would ever describe his words and actions as courteous or elegant, still Goose Barnacle never bullies the weak and always has a certain respect for his adversaries. He is even skilled at doing housework, so in essence he's completely different than his frightening appearance.
name: Goose Barnacle

descr: A little fox spirit with a fox mask and fangs on his chubby face. Actually, there are four in total, and they roll dice to determine who gets to take human form, while the three that lose take the form of foxes. They all four have different personalities, with the first being like a lazy cat, the second like an angel, the third like a noisy little overlord, and the fourth a wise-cracking intellectual.
name: Aburaage

descr: She has a lively and cheerful personality, and has always strived to become a true knight. Because she isn't a stickler for particulars, she usually plays well with others. She values her friends a lot and won't let her friends come to harm. She also has a soft side that others would never suspect of her, and is an extremely reliable partner. She likes to go roaming about and seeing lots of people and things.
name: Maple Syrup

descr: A profligate prince hiding from court disputes and living in seclusion in Reverie Valley. However, unable to give up his lavish lifestyle, he has built a luxurious mountain villa in his secluded spot.
name: Dongding Oolong

descr: A greedy, gluttonous gourmand that will eat until kingdom come. He finds the squabbles of the outside world a bit tiresome, so has chosen to reside in the paradise of the Capital teaching kids, writing poetry, gardening, and occasionally going on a journey. With his tremendous experience, he's seen it all, and in the critical moment, he is a dependable person. He also has a lot of seniority and is the Vice Master of the Castellan of the Capital.
name: Braised Dongpo Pork

descr: Calamus Wine is kind-hearted, with a cheerful personality. Because of her training as a doctor, she has no interest in the gender differences between men and women. She loves to research both medicines and poisons, and sometimes she even uses herbs to pull pranks on people. She believes that every herb has value and its own special purpose.
name: Calamus Wine

descr: Stand-offish and taciturn, this youngster gives a cold appearance, but is brimming with passion on the inside. He won't actively get close to others, but he remembers when others are good to him. He prefers using concrete actions to express himself rather than language. He prefers solitude and often researches magic books alone in his room.
name: Montblanc

descr: Formerly offered up to the Heretics as a human sacrifice, but then saved by Ginseng and allowed to stay in the Nether World. Because of past wounds, she no longer looks like a normal person, but to make herself look more normal, she gave herself two big, bright red cheeks. She puts up a fierce front to prevent people from bullying her, but she'll also protect the weak-looking Orecchiette.
