Due to her excessively lively and active personality, she was sent to the archives room to manage the archiving of documents. She's always irritable and loves to pretend to be a ghost and scare people.
name: Fermented Tofu

descr: A refined and genteel young man who always impresses everyone at first sight with his beauty and gives them an urge to protect him. Using his innocent exterior and gentle words as weapons, he teases out the most hidden secrets within the hearts of others. Those who don't know him think he's a perfectly courteous young man whom no one could dislike, but those familiar with him will find that his words can have a subtle venom that is hard to discern.
name: Finnish Reindeer

descr: As the Curator of Nanli Print Shop, he witnessed the birth of the shop. He is gentle and considerate, and always has a smile on his face. He is a gentleman adept at managing but still a little unpredictable. However, his sometimes overly-freewheeling way of doing things often has his subordinates caught off guard and shrugging their shoulders. For example, when he often skips out of the print shop to go have fun, or shuts himself up in his room reading comics.
name: Peking Shredded Pork

descr: Yellow Pea Cake is a vivacious and capricious Northern girl. She’s lively, enjoys messing around, and wherever she is, it’s sure to be a boisterous affair. However, due to her overly-frank and careless nature, sometimes she can make some cutting remarks that others don’t know how to take or even find extremely painful.
name: Pea Yellow

descr: Chiffon Cake is clever, cheerful, a bit of a chatterbox, and a tiny bit domineering. Born a noble, he is a man of simple ideas and enjoys the praise of others. In order to receive praise, he does things well, but he also has the unpraiseworthy fault of easily getting conceited.
name: Chiffon Cake

descr: Used to being doted on, she can be a little willful at times, but she's not a completely unreasonable young lady. She's usually quite tender and attentive, but if she gets set off, she will show a frightening side. She has a natural longing for and obsession with love, and looks forward to the day she meets her true love that will make her heart flutter. Although, because she's a Food Soul, this seems a bit unlikely, she still fervently believes and stays full of expectation.
name: Nougat

descr: Black Tea's Attendant raised a gun to their own head, ending it all. Having witnessed it all herself, Black Tea fell into a half-fallen state, for which she got hunted down by other countries as a Fallen Angel. As she escaped, she slayed Fallen Angels to make herself stronger, like a bloodthirsty demon.
name: Black Tea SP

descr: Originally modest and meek of character, ever since the passing of a certain Attendant and she began living in the temple, Adzuki Jelly gradually became upbeat and cheerful, like a true monk. She is clever and quick-witted, hard-working and diligent. She excels at observing, and although she doesn't say much, when she's happy, she'll squint her eyes together and reveal a smile. She rarely gets angry and has a composed, even temperament, but that doesn't mean she's emotionally shallow at all. She just always works hard not to let her emotions show, that's all.
name: Adzuki Jelly

descr: An overly-curious treasure collector who wants to get his hands on any and all treasure. He is well-versed in fengshui and exorcising demons, but he's still a little afraid of ghosts, so he's not all that reliable. In actuality, he doesn't love treasure that much, he just delights in the stories contained in each object's past. Once, several artifacts from a tomb connected together into a complete story, and that story shook him to his core so that he came to like these antiquities and would revisit their stories often.
name: Eight-Treasure Rice

descr: A little angel who considers herself weak because she can't grasp the essential of combat. She worships Takowasa. She used to be bullied because her form made humans think she was a water ghoul, and so she just adores Takowasa, who inadvertently saved her. She has taken it upon herself to care for his daily  needs (as a conch shell girl, she's very domestic). Her hair is her life, and when she's shy she'll hide behind it and turn into a green tangle of grass.
name: Seaweed Salad

descr: Does not often let his guard down around others, and protects himself with a body full of spikes. He has a dagger for a tongue and an explosive temper. Both in personality and appearance, he is positively flamboyant.
name: Sea Urchin

descr:
Pan de Muerto is the Spirit Guide of Nirvana funeral home, in charge of welcoming and seeing off the funeral home’s day-to-day clientele, of holding ceremonies for the departed, and holding celebrations at various times.
Her natural disposition is joyous and playful, but because of the nature of her daily work, she often has to struggle to control her facial expressions, put on colorful make-up, and express her sympathies to those who’ve lost a loved one with an air of sadness and composure (a struggle which occasionally is lost).
However, as soon as work ends, and no outsiders are around, Pan de Muerto can relax and resume being her usual joyous and fun-loving self.
name: Pan de Muerto

descr: A calm and composed person without much depth of emotion that lets all life drift by like clouds on the breeze, but also with a natural airheaded disposition that is unconcealable. A certain chain of events led to him losing his memories, and he is quite slow to react to things.
name: Soka Senbei

descr:
At first glance he seems kind, and even has a divine air about him, but in reality, he is an inveterate egotist.
Yokan has a special capability of sympathizing with the negative emotions of others, and because of this overpowering resonance, he always feels incredibly pained. To avoid this pain, he is obsessed with creating a world without sorrow, and to achieve this goal, he will stop at nothing.
name: Yokan

descr: Unwilling to take part in combat, but equally unwilling to let himself be disturbed by others, he is fairly territorial and only wishes to sleep peacefully inside his jar. But due to the special circumstances on Sakurajima, everyone is fighting for turf, so his hand is forced. At this time, he realized that he possesses uncommon combat ability, as well as a razor-sharp tongue.
name: Takowasa

descr:
Mojito sails the seas with a dream to find lost treasure.
The catalyst that got him into sailing was Rum, whose dashing manner drew him in. Mojito has held Rum as an idol ever since. Whenever Rum is mentioned, he becomes a starry-eyed little boy.
Mojito is a pure and kind fellow, although many humans are leery of getting close to him because of his appearance.
He says he doesn't mind, but on the inside, it really gets him down. So to avoid getting hurt, he calls himself an evil dragon and puts up a fierce front toward strangers in order to actively keep them at a distance... but he still can't help being kind here or offering help there.
As time went on, he became his current, disingenuous self.
name: Mojito

descr: Stollen Bread is followed by three reindeer sprites at her side, and the wheat in her basket brings people good prayers and wishes. She used to be called a present for the gods and is extremely likeable, treating those around her with warmth and care. Even after being used as a sacrifice, pure and good-hearted Stollen Bread still holds goodwill for this world. But she also sees clearly that the Church of Divine Grace has to some extent become a tool in the hands of certain people, so she has decided to put her faith in Donut and join the Grace Army, and thus continue to spread god's love to the people.
name: Stollen Bread

descr: A slender figure dressed head-to-toe in snow white, he is the mythic "White Impermanence" in charge of escorting souls into the underworld. He has a bubbly personality, fears nothing, and loves stirring up trouble. He always has a nefarious and fiendish grin on his face and holds a bowl of douzhi (a.k.a. mung bean milk) in his hand which he proffers to anyone he encounters.
name: Douzhi

descr: A stern and ascetic person who punishes what he considers to be evil with the most ruthless of methods. He would flinch at turning himself into a demon to punish evildoers, without any regard for whether they have their own troubles or good intentions. He metes out penalties in merciless cold blood, and even if his colleagues or he himself does wrong, he will punish without hesitation. He respects Ginseng a great deal, and actually he's normally quite agreeable and tender-hearted.
name: Fried Dough Strip

descr: Flower-Carved Glazed Fruit is a chipper young lady with a knack for carving intricate designs. After meeting Pian Er Chuan, she entered the Nanli Print Shop, where she continued to hone her craft. She might have a cheerful and ebullient personality, but she's also got a keen eye for details—not to mention a surprising amount of power.
name: Flower-Carved Glazed Fruit

descr:
A stern and serious patrolwoman who is no-holds-barred in the face of anyone who attempts to disrupt harmonious life and will not hesitate to draw her blade. She doesn't quite keep up with the fashions of the time, and when she speaks, she always ends up droning on and on in a lecture, so people complain that she's like an old-timer.
It's a criticism that gets her back up a bit.
name: Tamagoyaki

descr: Crab-Stuffed Orange is like an effusive little sun who is wont to cheer people up using all sorts of methods. He enjoys developing and modifying little machines and has crafted many marvelous and strange objects. Sometimes he'll even use his machines to play pranks on others. He has a treasure bag which contains numerous rare and wondrous baubles.
name: Crab-Stuffed Orange

descr: A child attendant of Ginseng who delivers commands and responses to others on Ginseng's behalf. He is a meek and mild little blind boy with an austere face, but his efforts to maintain his serious air is actually a little cute. Others mistakenly believe that Diting, the Ears of the Nether World, are his big cat, but in reality the one with the super hearing is actually him.
name: Orecchiette

descr: He's always friendly and agreeable, no matter what person or thing he's dealing with. Brioche knows many legends and stories of the ancient elves, and since his birth, most of his time has been spent living within an enchanted border cut off from the world. So, when he came to the real world, he was incredibly curious about everything and felt like everything was fresh and new. He believes in the gods of Tierra, and so he travels all over the place looking for traces of the gods.
name: Brioche

descr: The Vice Curator of Nanli Print Shop, who helps manage all the various affairs of the shop with high efficiency and ability. Although he's a direct, cold, and stone-faced person, he's really a softie on the inside and someone who considers others and cares for them, quietly taking care of many things for the shop. Due to their longstanding relationship, he is fully used to the Curator's propensity to go off on larks and disappear.
name: Pine Nut Wine

descr: Previously the earl of some Gloriville royal household, and although an incident with the Heretics caused a fall in station, he never placed much emphasis on his identity as an earl. He's a carefree, easy-going person and later joined the Grace Army because of the Heretic incident.
name: Earl Grey Tea

descr: A blustering exorcist who wields a hammer bigger than himself. He's a bit rash and naughty, but he can be obedient and is always full of vitality. He is one of the Five Good Omens, a symbol of hope. Legend says that anyone who sees him can find new hope even in their hour of despair.
name: Kirimochi

descr: A skinny and sickly-looking youth that manipulates a puppet. Because of prolonged life at the bottom of the sea, his eyes cannot see clearly, but he can use his sense of smell to distinguish Fallen Angels and Food Souls. He controls a beautiful little girl doll of about 12 years old. The doll holds a lantern that gives off spirit power which attracts Fallen Angels. He uses the little girl to attract Fallens, then kills them in cruel fashion.
name: Monkfish Liver

descr: One of the Dragon Palace Lord's most trusted guardians, he is cold, arrogant, and obstinate, never letting anyone not invited by the Palace Lord into Dragon Palace. As Amaebi's bodyguard, he is quite loyal and vigilant, but as Amaebi will tell you, he isn't much of a talker.
name: Kuruma Prawn

descr: The elder sister of Stargaze Rest, a gentle woman always dressed in a white shiromuku. Legends say that any who lay eyes on her will be blessed with happiness, and the mere sight of her makes one feel happy. She is an omen of good things and a symbol of happiness, and hopes that everyone can get along nicely together. If people don't get along nicely in front of her, she will get angry. She is a little bit wicked, as during leisure times she can fixate on the strangest things. Even the most boisterous of children get red in the face and shy when they see her.
name: Sekihan

descr:
After an evil human faction took him and performed modification experiments upon him, B-52 re-emerged as a merciless killing machine. He possesses great power and is utterly obedient to whatever "Master" he is programmed to follow.
When injured or being studied, he is immersed in a massive petri dish to rest.
name: B-52 SP

descr:
Laziji has a certain level of skill in mechanical techniques as well as magical prowess.
He wishes to establish a true paradise, a place where everyone can enjoy a safe and happy life. Laziji enjoys travel, and he often brings wounded Food Souls back to his home—and that's why the Capital grows larger every day. Anyone who dares encroach on his city will invoke his formidable wrath.
name: Laziji

descr: 外表生人勿近，但其实很好相处，不论什么请求，基本上都会接受。喜欢恐怖诡异的东西，但不包括人偶，看到人偶就想把它们都埋起来。热衷养生，由于自己身上的气味很刺激，所以嗅觉味觉不敏感，会出于善意让别人吃特别难吃但很健康的食物。
name: Salty Licorice

descr: The young princess of Dragon Palace is clever and crafty, and can be naughty but absolutely knows where the line is, so no one can ever get mad at her. She often takes advantage of her looks to pout and get what she wants, and there is always a bodyguard by her side assigned by the Palace Lord. The bodyguard is said to be for her protection, but more accurately is there to keep her from getting into too much trouble.
name: Amaebi

descr:
A free-wheeling scammer who sells counterfeit paintings all over the place. He'll make pals with whoever seems to be the big man on the totem pole, but then after he makes his money, he splits for greener pastures.
He is adept at making seals and paintings. The paintings he sells are all his own forgeries, which are quite faithful replicas capable of tricking all but experts. Moreover, if it's a painting that he made himself and stamped with his own seal, then he's able to eavesdrop on any noises in the vicinity of the painting.
Because he has no combat ability, he has no backbone around people who can really fight.
name: Square Mutton Fish

descr: Taken in by Pian Er Chuan as a scholar's assistant and disciple, Bean Paste Cake believes that Pian Er Chuan treats him quite well. He also loves ancient manuscripts, so he willingly stays around to study and work. Meanwhile, he's well-liked and cared for by many in the Print Shop for his friendly, industrious, and considerate personality.
name: Bean Paste Cake

descr: Ginseng secured himself inside of a giant magic array, using its boosting properties to extend his root whiskers to every corner of the world for gathering all kinds of information, like a data processing machine. That's why most of the time, he's processing information and doesn't wake up. He also helps within his limits to fix the constantly weakening mountain-river array. He is steady and dependable, and everyone finds him trustworthy. However, because of the array, he rarely appears in front of others, and most of the time he has Orecchiette deliver messages for him.
name: Ginseng

descr: Twice-Cooked Pork is a perfectionist with a calm and steady demeanor. He is highly skilled and capable, especially in the field of mechanical design. He was once rescued by Laziji, and then helped him to establish and operate his Capital city in a logical manner. Over time, the Capital became a safe haven for Food Souls.
name: Twice-Cooked Pork

descr: The current Lord of Dragon Palace, who was "raised" by the side of the former Lord King Crab. Capricious and hard to pin down, he is often haughty and strong-willed, making decisions that cause headaches for his subordinates. He is extremely obstinate about his plans and has an intense perseverance to press on no matter how arduous the road ahead. Because of some of his goals, he also doesn't mind holing up in the boring sea bottom. He clearly hates little children, and yet he positively dotes on Amaebi, seemingly because he has ulterior motives for her abilities.
name: Conpoy

descr: As an ancient painting restorer, she has superb skills and a passion for her work. She has a fairly high position in Nanli Print Shop, with a disciple who follows her named Bean Paste Cake. She often uses him to pass on messages for her. She seems stand-offish, but in private she has a soft spot for cute things, something only a very few people know about.
name: Pian Er Chuan

descr: He's often underestimated because of his height, but his clever brain is his greatest weapon. If anyone speaks ill of him, he'll grumble privately to himself, but he won't really hold a grudge. He helps others unconditionally, so he's often taken for a fool. When he really gets mad, he'll turn himself the size of a thumb and jump in a teacup, then row a little boat until he's too tired to remember what made him mad in the first place. His looks and personality are both cute, but his goal is to become cool.
name: Chawanmushi

descr: The boss of Stargaze Rest and one of the fabled Five Good Omens. He's so laid-back that he makes others impatient, but he plays his cards close to the vest. His idle demeanor makes him seem like an ordinary aristocrat with no combat ability, and any enemies that descend upon Stargaze Rest single him out as an easy target, but he's actually a formidable fighter. Although he often keeps people in suspense, he's actually quite dependable and can be decisive when he makes up his mind. Legends say that the sight of him will bring one luck for a time, and also riches.
name: Sea Bream Sashimi

descr: An innocent maiden who looks so ethereal, pure, and fairy-like that she seems sacred and off-limits. In reality, she's a creature who can become exceedingly infatuated and obsessed.
name: Ratatouille

descr: Cheery and passionate, with an extreme sense of justice, but naive almost to the point of foolishness. He used to be a patrolman, so he's physically fit. He can fight well, run fast, and is great at catching criminals. He saw some shady dealings inside the police department, so he left to pursue his own brand of justice, which brought him to the Sunset Agency.
name: Katsudon

descr: The true lord of Dragon Palace. After receiving sustained corrosion from the Poison of Acheron, before completely succumbing he handed his duties off to Conpoy and Kuruma Prawn, whom he "raised". But they did not obey his command and instead used the powers of Amaebi and the Jade Box to freeze him at the bottom of the sea.
name: King Crab

descr: He looks more aristocratic than the most blue-blooded noble, and more villain-ish than any dyed-in-the-wool villain, and yet he works for the good guys. Even when he's doing something ruthless, he always does so with a dazzling, handsome smile on his face. He can be a bit sadistic, but he is equally brutal to himself and his enemies. He is incredibly clear and determined about what his heart wants. He always has a jocular smile on his face and seems very good-humored and personable. He loves teasing Canned Sardines.
name: Brandy

descr:
Although her name is Burrito, she likes it when people call her "Taco" because she feels like it's more intimate, and she hopes to have all kinds of relationships with people. She loves to a good heart-to-heart and expressing feelings, and when a letter arrives, the flood of emotions that the recipient feels is what she thrives on.
That's why she chose to work for the post office and truly loves her job working with the carrier pigeons and delivering one emotion after another.
But the carrier pigeons have clashing personalities and often fight during downtimes on the job, which is a huge headache for Taco.
name: Burrito

descr: An enthusiastic and cheery, long-haired big sister-type who on first sight gives people the impression of being "Spanish sunshine in a bottle". In reality, she's prone to getting down on herself and is always on edge about not being better than her little brother in terms of abilities and all kinds of things. She's also got an unhealthy obsession over Champagne.
name: Sherry

descr: A feeble young girl with freakish strength who doesn't have the courage to talk to strangers and is wary of all things external. She has a fear of the unfamiliar, and if there are any vessels in her vicinity like or box or something big enough seal her up in, she'll instinctively want to hide in it. But in actuality, Rakugan's strength is powerful enough to smash boulders with her bare hands. But she is completely unaware of this and always thinks of herself as a weakling.
name: Rakugan

descr: Tartarmad, the strongest knight at Champagne's side, in charge of Champagne's own personal Food Soul army. People are often frightened by his ferocious demeanor, but he is a man true to his own beliefs, not caring for superficial appearances or socializing, a supremely loyal protector of the empire.
name: Tartarmad

descr: Haggis has been accompanied by hardship since the day he was born. But as pure as he is, even living in the midst of unhappiness, he still hasn't been devoured by despair. However, this also makes him gullible to anyone who is nice to him. He usually has a childlike innocence and energy, but under a certain kind of influence, he can sink into an extreme rage, and his Azazel will turn into a multitude of mountain goat heads that bite at his enemies.
name: Haggis

descr: She infiltrated the Eye of Horus's surveillance office under the guise of a maidservant, and although she may be clumsy as a maid, in combat she is a skilled expert. She is enthusiastic, cheerful, and outspoken. She's able to point out mistakes in the face of superiors and is like a caring big sister to everyone.
name: Creme Brulee

descr: Though this young woman may look gentle and quiet on the outside, she's actually got an intense fantasy life going on under the surface. In order to avoid suspicion from others about her overactive imagination, she often tries to keep an expressionless facade, but she often lets things slip. To cover up all this, she will use her powers to make people fall asleep. The observatory director Monaka will often detect her flights of fancy, but there's nothing she can do about him.
name: Hanabira Mochi

descr: A naturally evil youth with no sense of guilt. He has always firmly believed in a deity, but suddenly one day he learned the secret that the deity wants to kill all people. After being momentarily shaken up, he soon confirms with this "father's" guidance that the reason the deity wants to kill everyone is because this world has too much suffering and no hope. So, by killing everyone, the deity can send them all to a peaceful world without hardship.
name: Puff

descr: Tea Cake is a storyteller whose greatest hobby is finding people to tell stories to, but she always loves to keep the suspense and never finishes a story in one sitting. Not one to stand on ceremony, as long as she's got a table, she'll start telling a story anytime and anywhere. When telling her stories, she always acts out the parts of the characters in the book, doing the voices and mannerisms and everything. Aside from her talent for storytelling, in everyday life she's also a pro at telling deadpan jokes and is always saying things that leave people nonplussed.
name: Tea Cake

descr: Pufferfish Sashimi is obsessed with collecting and concocting all sorts of poisons, and he's also not above testing them on himself to see their effects. For this reason, normal drugs have basically no effect on him. His body is incredibly frail, and he looks like he could kick the bucket at any moment, but he has a fervent passion for poisoning himself half to death with his self-made concoctions that others find hard to understand.
name: Pufferfish Sashimi

descr: A Food Soul born together with Sherry. He might look a lot like his older sister on the outside, but their personalities couldn't be more different. Gin is exceptionally capable, but he's not enthusiastic and cheerful like Sherry. After being framed for a crime, he was locked up in the Tartarus Catacombs, after which his moniker "Gin" and his duties at The School were taken over by Sherry. This complicated his feelings for Sherry quite a bit.
name: Gin

descr: A prison guard who is stern, dutiful, and extremely conscientious. A stickler for the rules to an almost inhumane extent. But in life, he's a wholly innocent and naive youth. His all-too-serious demeanor causes him to take the jokes of others seriously. For example, he'll get tricked by criminals feigning illness, or be at a loss in the face of ridicule from others.
name: Canned Sardines

descr: A knight-errant who wanders all over in search of delicious food, and currently an employee in Grass Jelly's gaming tavern. He's a fan of spicy food, and although he may look arrogant and standoffish, he's a caring and innocent young man by nature who isn't good at expressing his feelings. When on the hunt for yummy eats, he certainly doesn't forget to help those that need helping, but he still can't quite get the hang of speaking from the heart.
name: Spicy and sour konjac

descr: A cold and dark exterior, with an extremely pure personality. He doesn't seem to give a care about anything, but he's actually quite kind and easily moved and just won't admit it. Because of an extreme inner sense of justice, he has no sympathy for evil people. However, sometimes he can be too black-and-white and seem to lack nuance.
name: Scone

descr: On the surface, he seems like a dawdling director of an observatory, always muttering incomprehensible things apropos of nothing and claiming they are divinations from the stars. But actually, as far as everyone could see, not one of these divinations ever came true, so they all started to write him off. In reality, his divinations are mostly accurate, and if some major unforeseen event happens to occur, he will think of a way to resolve it.
name: Monaka

descr:
Mysterious and dangerous, he is accompanied by a fierce-looking black qilin, and even when smiling, he gives off a vibe like he wouldn't touch you with a million-foot pole. He only does what he wants and can be somewhat mercurial.
From traveling the world, his breadth of knowledge is extensive. He knows a certain amount of truth about the world, but is unable to do anything about it, and he's tainted with the indifference of one that looks down from a great height. Ever the loner, he decided to give things one last try and returned to the land of his birth, the Light Kingdom, to establish Ghost Valley Academy and take up teaching whichever students fate brought his way.
name: Jinjunmei Tea

descr: Initially, Yu Qilin Tea was a renowned, fun-loving, hard-drinking, far-traveling, devil-horned person. After a certain experience that she doesn't want to think back on, she accepted the heavy responsibility to guard over Elusia, and her personality grew more dispassionate and composed. Although she still shows her capricious and stubborn side from time to time, she no longer readily shows a talent for governing the world and wishes only to live out her days in Elusia.
name: Yu Qilin Tea

descr: A young maiden always drifting along the valley like an ethereal spirit who likes lively scenes and socializing with others, but because she does not possess a corporeal body like other Food Souls, she's often mistaken for a ghost. Her outermost layer of clothing can change colors at will, enabling her to conceal herself. Discovering this little trick opened up a new avenue of fun for her, and she started using it to scare people all over the place. It wasn't until her valley got a new name — Ghost Valley — that she finally met someone willing to accompany her.
name: Jellyfish Salad

descr: A Food Soul from The Academy whom everyone dotes on. Every day she happily creates her own magic medicine with which she hopes to make everyone happy. Most of the time, the medicines she makes are sweet, but if she is feeling angry or sad, she'll make terrible candy. In her candy syrup, she can distill the best feelings of everyone but herself, which can then be preserved in the candy. That's why they say people can gain happiness from eating her candies.
name: Lollipop

descr: 费南雪善用谋略，精于计算，深谙弱肉强食的法则并将这一理念贯彻到底。她性格任性，没人能逼她做她不想做的事，但一旦她将你认作同伴后，性格就会温和不少，而且非常护短。费南雪凭借以物换物的特殊能力在贵族圈层很有名气，并因趣味相投而成了水果挞的密友，两人经常会相约一同喝下午茶。
name: Financier

descr: A Food Soul summoned by the Priest of the Cicada Wing Shrine in Sakurajima who was in charge of caring for the Sorceress and was extremely devoted to her. The humans killed the Sorceress to overthrow the rule of the gods, and Minazuki in turn killed those royal family members, after which he took up a life wandering in exile. As long as one doesn't get in his way, he is like an inexperienced young man who is kind and gentle to all. However, in order to exact revenge upon those humans that betrayed the Sorceress, he is ready to accept any punishment.
name: Minazuki

descr: Before joining Stargaze Rest, this newly-born Food Soul and well-protected little girl always felt a deep need to protect everyone else. She is one of the Five Good Omens and a favorite of the Divine Spirit who symbolizes familial peace and prosperity. Legend says that anyone who sees her will have very good luck for a whole year.
name: Kagami Mochi

descr: She has a fierce personality and wears her heart on her sleeve, which has led her to stir up no shortage of trouble. She speaks with a world-weary tone from all her youthful wanderings. Her origin is a mystery, the answer to which she has always been searching. After a certain mishap, she ended up in Reverie Valley and fell in love with the land and its people, staying there ever since.
name: Golden Thread Honey Date

descr: An innocent and mischievous little kid whose ignorance of the ways of the world gives her a stubborn and reckless attitude toward the outside world that gets her into innocuous little mishaps. Some people worship her for her 100% effective fortune-teller readings, so she proudly calls herself the Little Celestial.
name: Fortune Cookie

descr: A non-humanoid Food Soul with weak spirit power, she is always hiding alone under her large mushroom, pretending to be poisonous in order to protect herself. Her body is a gooey substance like a slime that takes a less-than-complete human form, but when afraid she will shrink into a corner and take on her original form: a mushroom-shaped white slime.
name: Cream of Mushroom Soup

descr: A lazy young optimist with a serious procrastination problem who will stop at nothing to put off writing her drafts. She is ditzy and flighty and always has a silly smile on her face that people just can't stay mad at, but she's actually kind of cunning. When it comes to things she's not interested in, she can't be asked; but when she does care, she'll go all out and won't rest or eat till she gets to the bottom of it.
name: Crispy Squab

descr: Reincarnated from the Xuanwu Emperor, who sealed himself within the mountain-river array, he has some of Xuanwu's memories, but he has forgotten his former companions. He only remembers his ambition to rule the world and to protect the Light Kingdom. He is unhappy at being seen as Xuanwu, but he approves of the things Xuanwu did and has a certain sympathy for the comrades who lost their monarch.
name: Baijiu

descr: A romantic and thoughtful lady of letters who is usually always in the library reading a book or organizing the stacks. She has a very rich and poetic inner world.
name: Yorkshire Pudding

descr: A sleepy pretty boy who seems to be able to fall asleep anytime. He always holds the name of his companion creatures, the Candied Wax Gourds, in his heart; and the two rarely are separated. He was born with a supple and delicate skin, but his personality is quite grumpy. If one accidentally wakes him when a drowsy spell is hitting him, or call him by the wrong name... one might get a blast of anger that hits much harder than a powder keg.
name: Sweetheart Cake

descr: A cheerful, valiant cowboy who has nothing but good intentions toward everyone. His hobbies are making friends and giving hugs. He's good-tempered, always in a good mood, and skilled at making others happy. However, he can get a little too enthusiastic and occasionally gets on people's nerves. He has a trusty horse named "Pineapple", and when he's got nothing else to do, he lugs people up onto the horse and goes for joyrides. Pineapple is a little temperamental, though, and doesn't like anyone except Churrasco riding him.
name: Churrasco

descr:
Pine & Crane Longevity is well-read and accomplished in painting and horticulture. After willingly accepting the mission to guard over Elusia, he assists Yu Qilin Tea in governing the realm. He appears to be mature and experienced, but in reality he is an innocent and pure person who is extremely easy to get riled up and agitated with a little teasing.
Meanwhile, precisely because he knows so much, he is a proponent of "slow and steady wins the race". This will often lead to conflicts between him and Yu Qilin Tea on certain matters, but as full of learning as he is, he can never win an argument against what he calls Yu Qilin Tea's "underhanded tactics".
name: Pine & Crane Longevity

descr: He thought he could stop it all from happening again, and that he would be the only one that would have to remember, but in the end, he was unable to change that rotten fairytale. Despite getting his hopes up countless times, he's still unable to truly believe that they can return to that time before. But fate seems to toy with him, making him run into that person in the least desirable ways. However, even though there is nothing left, that glimmer of light in his heart still hasn't been snuffed out.
name: Pizza SP

descr: She decided to work for Junmai Daiginjo as a way to repay him, but because of her shy personality, all she can do at first is cleaning work. Upon seeing a customer, she will quickly hide, only leaving behind a temari ball. In private, she's actually a chatty Cathy.
name: Edamame

descr: Cinnamon Roll gives off a natural scent. She has a passion and a merciful heart for all of creation; and although she knows she's feeble, she still does everything in her power to help others. Her exotic scent has the ability to control people's minds, but Cinnamon Roll usually only uses it to put to sleep those not long for this world, providing them a last bit of comfort in their lives and removing as much regret as possible. Although she's a rare "normal person" amidst the "carnival", she also has a skittish personality and is easily embarrassed. When she gets complimented, she'll put her own self out with her cinnamon stick, and even go into a hibernation-like state where she lays dormant for days and days.
name: Cinnamon Roll

descr: A lover of all things good and delightful, and an ardent admirer of beauty. Wherever he goes, he brings swirling mists, the call of birds, and the scent of flowers. He says only a spring day full of blooming flowers can motivate him to go outside, but that's only because the spring season has many of the flowers and herbs that he requires for making incense. He believes different scents bring different feelings of beauty, which is why he approaches the concocting of incense with an uncommon fervor and exactitude.
name: Biluochun

descr: The manager of Revelry Casino. She likes to make bets to get her kicks, not for the money but for the thrill of extreme risk. She's the type who follows her heart and seizes the day, and never drinks water when there's wine to be had. She often says things on purpose to stir up trouble because she loves to see people get angry and hurt. She is like a villain in a drama.
name: Blini

descr: A gentle and elegant royal princess who loves playing chess and can sit quietly all afternoon in the garden analyzing a position on the board. She abides by the norms of the royal court when conducting herself in society and is therefore supremely sure of herself when it is time to act. She is treated respectfully by every successor king as their nation's ever-exalted princess. Meanwhile, Battenberg Cake is also seen as a lucky star able to bless marriages with happiness, for which lovers often come to her for her blessing. Whether for commoners or members of the royal court, Battenberg Cake always gives her sincere blessing.
name: Battenberg Cake

descr: Although she hasn't reached that age yet, she has an intense yearning for the day she will don the bridal veil, and she's prone to romantic flights of fancy. Meanwhile, she'll show her comparatively "violent" side to her childhood sweetheart Zhuang Yuan Hong—who often bursts her fantasy bubbles. Also, when it comes to alcohol tolerance, she is somehow a bit more capable than Zhuang Yuan.
name: Nu Er Hong

descr: The seventh teacher at The School, in charge of "Survival" class. He is grim-looking and incredibly imposing, but he has a simple heart. If anyone is good to them, he will be obedient to them in every way. Even if they're only being superficially nice to him, he will give everything he's got to repay them. Ignorant of the world, he was accustomed to living a barbaric life in the polar region of Aectis. He isn't accustomed to life in the outside world and is surprised when people see him as a frightening ghoul. When news of him reached The School, Finnish Reindeer was given the order to bring him back.
name: Kiviak

descr: The auctioneer of Revelry's auction house, "Devil's Hole", and also the owner of Revelry's treasure shop, "Dragon's Lair". Her hobby is collecting rare and precious objects, then putting them up for auction and using the money to get even more treasures. She's a born performer who turns the auctions she hosts into operas. She is effusive in both word and deed, and her excessive ebullience often leaves people scratching their heads. But at the critical moment, she always goes MIA and only occasionally can be relied upon when it's a matter of life and death.
name: Red Velvet Cake

descr: An indolent youth who hates work but will feign being a mature and earnest hard worker in front of Pesto Pasta, whom he adores. He is a straight-shooting little brat who gradually shows a softer, more innocent side under the influence of the people in the Revelry organization.
name: Caesar Salad

descr: An assassin capable of assuming the guise of anyone and known as The Faceless. But what he likes more than anything is to dress up like his victim and live as his "doppelganger", to the point that there's an urban legend going around that if you see your doppelganger, it means you don't have long to live. He has his own theory of assassination aesthetics, and he'll let his assassination target see their "doppelganger" days before he intends to kill them.
name: Lasagna

descr: A golden-haired youth with the nickname "Killer Rabbit", the first time he ever took up arms was for a fairly pure cause—to avenge his former attendant who was mercilessly exploited and oppressed and to fight the bloodthirsty nobles. But as time has pushed on, the increasing scope of what he considers crimes has him confused about his original intentions.
name: Welsh Rarebit

descr: Grants people life, and then capriciously strips it of them, leaving behind just an empty room stinging with the smell of ammonia. Hakarl is active in corners hidden from the light, and her beaming smile means another slaughter is coming. Even so, there are still people who are willing to chance it. After all... who doesn't yearn for the life of immortality that she promises?
name: Hakarl

descr: A pretty-looking young man with a sincere personality and an uncanny propensity for getting lost. Although born into the opulent palace of the Northern Dynasty, he has no stomach for all that intrigue and deception. After deciding to leave, he accidentally gets lost and arrives in the paradise-like Elusia. Having found his ideal land, Ruyi Roll decided to stay on this mysterious enchanted island.
name: Ruyi Roll

descr: Borodino was born on the battlefield and has been called the goddess Death by mortals because she's often wandering around mass graves. She used to live life like a wild beast on the battlefield, and so she has a healthy respect for nature and severely punishes those who would harm or scorn nature. She is currently the cafeteria manager of Revelry. Although her scythe can cut down souls, usually it is only used for hunting animals and harvesting vegetables.
name: Borodino

descr: His burly body, imposing aura, and booming voice often get people to think he's a scary individual; but in reality, he's so simple and innocent that people take him for a fool. Focaccia is like a walking furnace who raises the temperature wherever he goes. He also naturally becomes the focus of everyone's attention. As the leader of "Red Flame", he infiltrated "Revelry" trying to track down the people that cheated him. He thinks he's staying undercover, but everyone sees right through him. His excessive enthusiasm is always giving people headaches, but he'll never give up trying to help. Optimism is his strong point.
name: Focaccia

descr: Born in the extreme cold of Aectis, he can freeze objects with his touch, which comes in handy when he's mixing drinks on the rocks. He was sold by the villagers of Aectis to Nevras and later saved by Pesto Pasta, whose place he took managing Revelry. He looks as beautiful and impassive as a glacier, but in reality he's a powder keg. The people in Revelry secretly call him Big Devil, and his method of teaching others a lesson is usually to let them "cool down" a bit.
name: Alaskan Ice Cream

descr: A young man born in the slums of Palata, his cheery disposition has garnered him many friends in the slums, friends whom he protects with his pair of swords. He was born of a conflict between the denizens of the slums and the royal family, from which he gets to know the crown prince and his own story begins to unfold.
name: Shawarma

descr: A little princess as exquisite as a doll who is esteemed and adored by the kingdom's subjects but has become taciturn and sullen from suppressing her natural inclinations too much. Actually, she has a side of her personality that is just like a normal little girl.
name: Princess Cake

descr: Bouillabaisse seems like an otherworldly fairy, lacking in common sense but yearning to help others. Because of this, it's difficult for him to avoid doing bad things out of good intentions. The fishbones on his body can be used as weapons, but also to make wish talismans for customers. The sight of him plucking a bone from his body is a brutal one, but every time, he doesn't seem to mind one bit. What he likes doing most is soaking in a hot springs, but he doesn't tolerate heat well. Once he almost passed out in the hot springs and was saved by a devoted customer. He is good-tempered, to the point that he was almost sold at auction and didn't get mad. He even happily asserted how wonderful it would be if he fetched a good price.
name: Bouillabaisse

descr: The "Beast" of the Pit, Revelry's boxing ring. A lover of pain, the more he hurts, the harder he fights. But although he may fight like a madman, normally he's no different from any other youngster. If anything, he's even more innocent and naive. He loves delicious foods, especially sweets, and he loves stuffing whatever he sees into his mouth to have a taste. Because of his painful past, he doesn't like being by himself, so he'll often bug people into fighting him.
name: Ganache

descr: Once a cold-blooded, merciless mercenary, on one mission she encountered the people of "Specter", who had not yet become a family, and she stuck around for various reasons. After the war, she made the decision to become the family's maid, but she doesn't seem to have any of a maid's conscientiousness. She's not only always making the young master of the house cry, she also harasses the butler, Chicken à la King, who is at least on paper her superior. For her, the joy of being a maid has never been in her master's satisfied smile, but in satisfying her own lust for power in setting her master's daily agenda.
name: Wiener Schnitzel

descr: As a Food Soul "manufactured" by a special process in the Academy, Tomahawk Steak never paid much regard to the contracting binding him. To him, the pain of not being able to do things according to his wishes is harder to bear than the backlash of the contract. Be that as it may, for his comrades, he still decided to carry out that "mission" that the humans forced upon him. He may seem impulsive and belligerent, but his temperament is actually incredibly stable. He usually won't act rashly, and before his comrades, he even shows an extraordinarily childish side. Ever since the war, he'll occasionally let a look of exhaustion slip out, but his habit of getting drowsy seems to have another reason...
name: Tomahawk Steak

descr: Although he seems elegant and refined, he's actually screw-up who often bungles his tasks. For example, kitchen explosions and burned bed sheets are common occurrences. But every time, he tries to cover it up with a composed demeanor until he can hurriedly try to clean up his mess. Even so, he has always believed that he can become a consummate butler, a goal which he always works hard to achieve.
name: Chicken à la King

descr: Although she looks like a violent thug, she's got a surprisingly good head on her shoulders. It's just that it's hard for her to control her emotions, and once she is ignited into a rage, she goes berserk. She doesn't have much common sense about life, but she also never sweats the small stuff. Even if her arm got chopped off, this berserker would just smile and keep fighting. She is extremely forgiving of her family members, and she knows that Pandoro secretly trains for combat, so she occasionally helps her with special lessons.
name: Rachel Sandwich

descr: His attendant was the proposer of the Tartarus plan. In the ensuing power struggles, Zabaione was forced to play the part of a cynical playboy, gallivanting through social occasions gathering intel for his attendant. After the plot to murder his attendant, he killed every last one of the enemy side and fled to Tartarus. To the people on the outside, he's a prisoner of Tartarus, but to those on the inside, he's their protector.
name: Zabaione

descr: A tsundere that likes to play the hero. She's afraid of pain, but she also feels ashamed to be seen as weak by others, so she'll pretend like it's nothing. However, her acting skills aren't very good, and all kinds of people see right through her, which makes her hopping mad. She's the little sister that everyone loves to dote on.
name: Pandoro

descr: Not longer after Casatta was summoned, he was taken advantage of and betrayed by his Attendant. Although he was supposed to die on the spot, a joke of fate led him into Pizza's kingdom. Just as no one placed any hopes in him from the start, he didn't trust anyone either. It wasn't until the sunlight shining on fields of daisies slowly pierced his own heart that he finally started to cherish this fairytale life of fantastic beauty.
name: Casatta SP

descr: The young master of the Specter family, he often pouts and pretends to be pathetic, but he's actually extremely mischievous. He especially likes scaring people with pranks, and Chicken à la King is often the target of his schemes. But to be honest, Deviled Egg is extremely timid and is often scared to tears by Wiener Schnitzel.
name: Deviled Egg

descr: A calm rationalist who thinks like a robot, always seeking logic and disregarding emotion, which leads others to see him as cold-blooded. He has a genius-level mind and is the only Food Soul among the researchers at the Academy. After a certain incident, he made the decision to leave the Academy and found Revelry, where he now observes what changes will be wrought in the world when he grants freedom and power to some lunatic Food Souls. He's always muttering to himself as if talking to someone, but what he says is often opaque and impenetrable, such as saying this world is just a game and things like that. Although he has an uncommon intellect, he is a fool about life; and if left to his own devices, he could very well spend his whole life cooped up in a lab.
name: Pesto Pasta

descr: A part of the control group of a Food Soul experiment, and so more free and relaxed than other experiment subjects, making him an energetic youngster. At the beginning, he had no idea how cruel the experiment was, until one day he happened to see Feta Cheese. Out of his sense of kindness and justice, Tiger Skin Cake decided to protect him, and he escaped the laboratory with him. Although not very strong himself, he always pretends to be fierce in order to protect Feta Cheese. When he gets hurt, he never makes a peep and will only furtively wipe tears from his eyes. His pure-heartedness prevents him from seeing the strange possessiveness Feta Cheese displays toward him. He just steadfastly tries to protect him.
name: Tiger Skin Cake

descr: A cutie with the looks of an angel who is a bit of a coward due to a bitter history of being experimented on. Although essentially kind, he'll turn obsessive and crazed at anything having to do with Tiger Skin Cake. Tiger Skin Cake is the first person to ever truly be friends with him, and also the first person to protect him, so he depends on Tiger Skin Cake and is fairly possessive about him. Sometimes he will "blacken" because of Tiger Skin Cake and use the possibility of his Falling to get his hooks into Tiger Skin Cake.
name: Feta Cheese

descr: One of the five Good Omens, she can change her external appearance at will, so her true appearance and even gender are a mystery. She mostly takes the form of a young maiden, but in contrast to her looks, Kanburi is steeped in all knowledge, past and present. However, she doesn't like showing this off and risk getting tangled up in pesky situations.
name: Kanburi

artifactName: Chicken Feet with Pickled Peppers Core
descr: When sick, his body gradually turns translucent, except for his right hand which isn't affected. He also treasures his beautiful hand because of his skill in painting. Chicken Feet with Pickled Peppers likes wearing white and is a bit of a clean freak and skittish around blood. When working, he is diligent and strict, but the tenderness he has for his acquaintances belies his stern appearance. He sometimes floats silently behind his companions and scares them, then pretends like nothing happened with a straight face.
name: Chicken Feet with Pickled Peppers

descr: Likes to give himself a persona, usually forcing himself to be a cold and austere swordsman, although in reality he's very kind and helpful. He likes acting as a mediator and gets things done in a direct, no-nonsense manner. He's a firm believer that actions speak louder than words. He usually keeps a tight lip in order to keep up his facade, but he'll prattle to his weapons on the sly.
name: Raincoat Cucumber Salad

descr: On many levels, he's the Specter family's most dependable member. He has a sharp mind and is a king of calculating and logic. He actually has a bad temper, but because the other members of his family all have bad tempers, he has to contain his own fits of anger, the consequence of which is that he does some abnormal things when alone. His eyes can see some scenes from the future, but he himself does not enjoy having this ability, so he usually wears glasses. His soul pendulum has a hypnotizing effect, but Reuben feels this effect too, so he rarely uses it. Usually he just uses it as a projectile weapon.
name: Reuben Sandwich

descr: At first sight, she looks like an ethereal fairy, but this impression is obliterated as soon as she opens her mouth. She has a vixenish and brash personality, and although she's actually gentle and kind, she is stubborn too, never allowing anyone to question her decisions. However, in order to save someone's life, even a complete stranger's, she would unflinchingly sacrifice her own flesh.
name: Dunhuang Dogbane Tea

descr: The future heir to Abaidos and a worry-free young prince. He loves sunshine and fresh flowers, so he often sneaks out of the gloomy castle. He always gets scolded for his fun-loving ways, but he never thinks about changing. He is firm in his ideas, and to a certain extent is a bit of a rebel.
name: Qatayef

descr: He scams people into writing their wishes on his ema placards with the promise they will come true, but really he's just using the horse to gather wish power in an attempt to traverse the Gate of Acheron and leave Sakurajima. Not only will the humans who write their wishes on the horse not have them come true, they'll actually bring about the opposite effect of their wish.
name: Castella

descr: With his cold, sullen appearance, he's always giving off a vibe that says "stay away". He's got an aloof personality that's also unpretentious in a way that people find mystifying. He has an intense curiosity, and if he wants to do something, he'll always find a way to get it done. He was born feeding on the fear of humans, so he's often following and scaring them, but he can't stand noise, so he doesn't allow his victims to scream. He often uses tentacles instead of his hands to accomplish all kinds of things, and his left hand seems inhabited by some kind of creature.
name: Schupfnudeln

descr: A carefree little princess who may be a little mischievous but is kind and thoughtful at heart, which is why everyone in the palace loves this little cutie. Aside from loving sweets, Eton Mess is also keen on children's stories. Her innocent romanticism and imagination, coupled with some intense curiosity, have opened the doors for her to a fairytale-like magic world.
name: Eton Mess

descr: She has a gentle and dignified appearance and always stays calm and collected no matter what happens. She is decisive when taking action and will show a cold, even merciless side when protecting her people. At her core, though, she isn't a bad person.
name: Sticky Toffee Pudding

descr: Eternally sunny and cheerful, with apparently inexhaustible energy, he's a pure spirit who easily believes in others and likes to get along with people. He is also kind and brave, with a sense of justice rivaling anyone. His firmly held ideals will lead him to do things one might call crazy, like spout nonsense with a look of complete innocence and seriousness, but he pulls it off because he is a genius actor. He will come right out and say what's on his mind, but his excessive candor sometimes offputs people.
name: Souvlaki

descr: One of the Food Souls created by the Academy. His ears and tail are a product of their experiments, and they remind him of painful Academy memories, which is why he feels unhappy and hurt if anyone ever calls him a horse. He has a gentle, kind personality; but occasionally he'll have negative thoughts. He often worries that something unfortunate will happen, which is why he's always breaking out into tears.
name: Vanilla Muffin

descr: He likes to use rockets to take care of troublesome people or situations and acts in a high-key and odd manner, which leaves people bewildered. He is an alcoholic with a poor tolerance for the stuff, but he loves enjoining people to drink with him. Meanwhile, he'll ask his drinking buddy likes the drink or not, and if they say it's not good, he offs them. If they say they like it, he'll go crazy and make them drink till they die. However, the majority of drinking buddies that have died at his hand were all Fallen Angels.
name: Shochu

descr: He has the look of a god of all creatures but is not truly a deity. He takes pity on the troubles of the world and does all he can to protect the land, but still he becomes a target for human anger because he's unable to save everyone. Over a long period of time, he has learned to be indifferent. But when the even more merciless cold of winter is at hand, he can't resist creating a warm spring environment for innocent creatures, even if he has to face the bone-chilling cold of the winter by himself.
name: Moussaka

descr: This young maiden dressed as a samurai is referred to as one of the Seven Great Tall Tales. Legends say she makes people's wishes come true and then ruthlessly kills them, and that the red of her kimono is from blood stains, but no one actually knows the real truth. She treasures her blades and believes that blood will keep them sharp and well-maintained, which is why she often goes out hunting at night.
name: Kamaboko

descr: He has an open and cheery disposition, and although he looks frail, he actually has lots of strength and stamina, capable of flying to faraway places to carry out missions. Influenced by the Nanli Print Shop's worship of the divine beast Rosefinch, Dong'an Chicken is also an extreme devotee of Rosefinch. The vision of restoring Rosefinch to his divine place is etched into his heart.
name: Dong'an Chicken

descr: Contemptuous of her original Attendant's excessive desire for fame and money, she started depending on her own ability to acquire knowledge, gradually turning into the person she is today, indifferent to fame or material gain. Her only desire is to live long enough to see how this world will evolve.
name: Duck Confit

descr: An experimental product of the Academy with childlike innocence and devilish cruelty. With his clever brain and surpassing combat ability, everything around him is capable of being turned into a weapon. He has practically never met his match. To shed the restraints of his contract and escape the Academy, he injured his own brain and lost his memory, becoming a free "madman". Although he later restored his memory and intellect with the help of his creator, the damage was still irreversible, and there's still the risk that he'll suddenly lose control. Meanwhile, in order to secure the trust of a certain dangerous person and attain his goal, Cheddar Cheese must continue feigning madness.
name: Cheddar Cheese

artifactName: Lotus Root with Sticky Rice Core
descr: An obedient child with nice manners, pure kindness, and an adult-like, quiet demeanor. Not wanting to cause trouble for others, she doesn't make a fuss even in the face of trouble or distress. Rather, she just cries quietly to herself. Lotus Root with Sticky Rice is not only an excellent cook, she's also proficient in calligraphy and doesn't mind sharing. She's like a thoughtful little angel that everyone in Ghost Valley Academy dotes on.
name: Lotus Root with Sticky Rice

descr: An ambitious schemer with a frightening vision. The things he wants to do may be insane, but his extraordinary charisma always gets people to follow him willingly. His every word and deed is full of elegant nobility, and he gives off a vibe that is tender and gentle, never uncomfortable or aggressive. This only makes it easier for him to obtain the trust of others, even though he has seemingly never trusted anyone. For Kaiserschmarrn, the loyalty and safety of companions is of course important, but danger and challenge are better at rousing his desire to conquer.
name: Kaiserschmarrn

descr: Beneath a soft and feeble exterior is a hard head that would rather die than bow down to anyone. To strangers, he can be a little cold and aloof, but inside he's still like a little kid trying to act cool on purpose. Although born of humble origins, he's never stooped to servitude and flattery. He's vowed to achieve his aims on his own in his search for true freedom and a simple, happy life.
name: Feijoada

descr: A young man whom everyone finds reliable and is always affable no matter when, although Nu Er Hong's presence brings out his teasing side. Zhuang Yuan Hong firmly believes that if those with power shoulder the responsibility, then this world can become a better place. What may surprise people, though, is that his tolerance for alcohol isn't better than Nu Er Hong's.
name: Zhuang Yuan Hong

descr: A straight shooter who will always come out and say when he's unhappy and will get his vengeance if you cross him. Most of the time, he is stern and serious, but he also has a boyish side. He finds splitting into factions and infighting to be too much of a bother, so he has chosen to hitch his wagon to the smartest person he can find. He goes along Kaiserschmarrn's every plan unconditionally, even if he doesn't understand his cruel orders.
name: Pastilla

descr: This stern and serious young man into "ikebana" (Japanese flower arranging) is a like the director of an observatory. He places heavy emphasis on doing things by the book, and if a plan formulated for others is ruined, he will start sermonizing. However, the others in the observatory often do unreasonable things that really give him a headache. The potted plants around him are living things that become uncommonly active when they leave their pots.
name: Nerikiri

descr: Passionate, cheerful, and pure-hearted, she is a devotee of dancing and positively loves teaching the art to others. In order to learn a dance properly, she will go research the local culture and customs, which has made her an expert in the ways of places all over the world. She was always partial to the culture of the Light Kingdom and harbored a yearning to go there, as well as the aspiration to spread the dances of her own home. As fate would have it, she just so happened to receive an invitation to be an instructor at the Ghost Valley Academy. From there, she became a "goddess" in the hearts of the academy's students.
name: Snow-capped Volcano

descr: A famous clothing designer in the Light Kingdom who previously studied abroad in Gloriville but still loves the ancient classical style of the Light Kingdom more. She is especially fond of stage costumes and hopes to fuse innovative tailorings and materials with classical forms so that more people can appreciate the classical beauty of the Light Kingdom. She is a very wealthy young mistress who has never been stingy with money. She spends freely and is fawned over by practically every merchant, but Million Dollar Stew is no ingenue—when it comes to doing business, she never takes a loss.
name: Million Dollar Stew

descr: When his belly's full, he's all smiles; but when he's hungry, he becomes shrewd and destructive. However, even when he's roaring, he always has a smiling face. This sometimes frightens people, but honestly he's just a kid who simply wants to protect his friends and fill his belly.
name: Tiger Salad

descr: Although he's wearing a cute skirt, he's actually a boy. A mascot-like member of Hearsay Pavilion, he craves familial affection. The Proprietress is like a mother to him, and he is willing to do anything she commands. He uses his bells to lure little girls who have lost their way in the mountains to play with him, then he takes them back to Hearsay Pavilion to listen to the Proprietress tell stories.
name: Salmon Oyakodon

descr: Now the leader of the Fantasy Opera Troupe, Mousse used to be an exemplary aristocratic Food Soul who lost an excessive amount of spirit power after an unfortunate incident with a taboo ritual. This did irreparable damage, and the only thing that kept him alive is a seed from an elven tree. During an emergency with the opera troupe, an explosive spirit power was awakened in him through his powerful will and conviction to safeguard his friends even unto death. He briefly was restored to his original form and resolved the troupe's crisis.
name: Mousse SP

descr: As a travel photographer that has been all over Tierra, he enjoys making a record of his travels by taking photos of Tierra's various sights. He enjoys the wandering lifestyle and looks like a dissolute playboy, but he also seems to have a mysterious past.
name: Prosciutto di Parma

descr: With an uncommon love for archeology, she often flies into a rage over academic questions of antiquity. Although frightening when enraged, she's normally a well-spoken and cheerful young lady. However, she doesn't take much interest in cutesy things. Her eyes only light up when she sees antiques, ancient tombs, or desiccated remains. She gets very focused when restoring antiques and won't react to any person or thing in the outside world. She just keeps her stamina up with a steady supply of sweets as she works tirelessly on her restoration, smiling the sweetest smile when her work is finished.
name: Caramel Macchiato

descr: With his gruff exterior and unruly, rebellious streak, he always seems to rub people the wrong way. However, on the inside, he's actually quite gentle and conscientious. Because of a bet he made with Feylamairre, he went about the task of finding a successor for the great magician with utmost earnestness. Although he doesn't know a thing about magic, he's got strong instincts. Most magicians are no match for him, and on the inside he actually looks down a bit on magic.
name: Bresse Chicken Soup

descr: A young woman with a special physical makeup which causes any object she touches to wither away. To escape this curse-like condition she was born with, Pu'er came to Elusia to seek a solution. Eventually, she found an hourglass that can rewind time three minutes. However, Pu'er is forced to stay in Elusia now so as not to interfere with the mortal world.
name: Pu'er

descr: Brought from her own country by a princess married off to the country of Wrathlowe, she sailed across the sea. Being far from her hometown, at first she didn't fit it. After her Attendant passed away, she received an invitation from Battenberg Cake to join their tea party group as the sole member who was merely an aristocrat and didn't bear the title of princess.
name: Angel Food Cake

descr: He was once imprisoned by an evil magician and trained with cruel methods such as being thrown amongst a pack of wild beasts. This terrible torture brought out his latent ability, and it was all in the service of creating a tool that would just follow orders. Panna Cotta makes no distinction between good and evil, knows nothing of ordinary life, and has only lived the life of a beast.
name: Italian Panna Cotta

descr: A sexy demoness that loves art and enjoys being Fallen. Externally, she looks like an elven fairy, but her heart is gloomy and evil. Her biggest goal is to guide an artist to create a great work of art, even if it's an exquisite murder.
name: Absinthe

descr: A youngster with an inscrutable mind who always seems wreathed in a foreboding aura. He seems able to see into the minds of others and often claims himself to be their mind's murkiest shadow. However, in actuality, he just relies on his ability to turn invisible to frequently observe others; although he truly is adept at deducing what people are thinking. As cunning and calculating as he is, though, he's still a child at heart. He'll get into big arguments with people over trifling matters, and he's always mocking and teasing others. He may not be able to distinguish right from wrong so well, but he never does anything that goes against his will.
name: Qamar al-Din

descr: Friendly and kind to everyone without exception, he is a Food Soul magician with the best reputation in Savoy. His flames are the gentlest around, and practically no one has ever seen him angry. But his true self is actually extremely anxious and irritable. He only stuffs down his anger to maintain appearances with everyone, then he flies into a rage on the inside when he's alone.
name: Iberian ham

descr: This expedition team leader has wit and swagger, but he can also be a bit too brash with his words. He's unrestrained in his actions to the point of being excessively free, always cooking up wildly imaginative plans that bring his team no end of suffering. However, as arduous as the journey may be, the result is always a good one. His Attendant is the Seer of Abaidos, who left behind a lot of vague prophecies before his untimely demise. After inheriting his book of prophecies, Baklava learned of a terrible secret and left Abaidos. He's gone all over the world trying to decode the book's contents in a search for the deeper truths about this world.
name: Baklava

descr: With her intense and difficult-to-restrain emotions, she will turn whatever thing or person she likes into foam in an attempt to always be with them, which is also the reason she became a wanted criminal. Although she looks like a naughty girl who doesn't want to go home, she actually has trouble staying up late and is usually asleep by eight or nine o'clock.
name: Café au Lait

descr: A young nobleman who inherited the Saskatoon Toy Factory and has a story of loneliness hiding underneath his spoiled and willful facade. Lacking in "love", Saskatoon Berry Pie yearns for a constant companion. Even if that means dancing with Death, he would swallow that bitter pill like it was candy.
name: Saskatoon Berry Pie

descr: Heaven Manufacturing is an innovative company striving to work with various large enterprises and factories to weave a beautiful, heavenly dream for their workers and clients. The founder of Heaven Manufacturing, Vidal Ice Wine comes across as gentle and refined, and even a bit cute. Compared to his collaborators, he can make one feel as if they've been good friends for years. However, the true face of this young and talented entrepreneur isn't known to many. The moment you hand over your trust to him, you've stepped into his meticulously laid trap.
name: Vidal Ice Wine

descr: Born with a hard-to-control urge to destroy, although if one did manage to get close to him, they could get along no problem. He enjoys piers, and he likes sitting on piers, dazing off, and eating french fries even more. Comic books are another of his daily pastimes, although he's not a devotee. He doesn't like how the main characters in comic books are always so passionate and hard-working, so he draws his own. Unfortunately, his drawings are absolutely terrible.
name: Moules Frites

descr: She easily gives people a sense of closeness and seems like a gentle and cheery lady on first impression, worthy of one's trust. But that's all an illusion. The real Montreal sees everyone as stepping stones on her path to success, tools for achieving victory. Montreal also holds grudges, and she is extremely strict with her time. If someone is late even ten seconds, she will write a curse on them in her little notebook. They're mostly not lethal curses, but it's still a little frightening how she laughs while she curses people.
name: Montreal Smoked Meat

descr: Came to the continent of Radiance as an outsider on a mission, only to find herself in danger. Cold on the outside, Milk does not ignore the suffering of others
name: Milk SP

descr: A little prince born with a silver spoon. Although he always shows a proud and rude side, for instance ordering people around that he's only just met and saying spiteful things, if the other person just indicates that they don't like this, he'll become much more polite. Like a princess from The Princess and the Pea, he's got all manner of hang-ups. He'll go nuts if there's even a grain of sand in his bed. However, in order to hang out with Shawarma, he'll grit his teeth and slum it even if it means he's got dark circles in his eyes the next day. He's got a bit of a teenager complex and has a cheesy way of speaking that Shawarma either mocks mercilessly or ignores, which incites Falafel's aristocratic rage.
name: Falafel

descr: As a Food Soul without a heart, Macaroni has no choice but to eat human hearts to stay alive. He despises his fate as a villain, and precisely because of this, although he looks crazed and dangerous on the outside, Macaroni has an inner determination not to engage in any other depraved acts. But then when he meets that "toy" that fears loneliness, he's again forced to become a plaything in Fate's hands again.
name: Macaroni

descr: Devoid of emotion, without any likes or dislikes, this little girl of doll-like beauty can occasionally sense concern for her from others and so shows them a certain amount of care too, but that's as far as it goes. As far as she's concerned, humans, animals, and those eternally happy toys in the toy factory are all the same. Moreover, getting too close to her may bring misfortune.
name: Pavlova Cake

descr: Refined and gentle, and exceedingly wise, but with a weak constitution. Although a chronic invalid, he is the only Food Soul in Easthedge Nation who dares raise his voice in an argument with Agate Fish Ball. Usually his temper is fine, but he'll blow his top if there's any matter involving Agate Fish Ball. In the early days of Easthedge's formation, it was entirely due to his painstaking work that the country was healed. He is the only reason Easthedge is around today, and he's the only person Agate Fish Ball can truly rely on.
name: Walnut Porridge

descr: Born in the abandoned temple of the Divine Lord White Tiger, summoned by the barren, yet intense "Power of Hope" of a beleaguered people. Agate Fish Ball's heart yearns for a prosperous state and peaceful populace, just like the numerous commoners, but inside her also roils the tyrannical blood of the white tiger. Beneath her generous and swaggering exterior is a will of uncommon obstinacy, which is how she was able to get all those bloodthirsty and warlike souls under her thumb in the first place. Rather than just start a dynasty, Agate Fish Ball quite cares for her people. However, she knows well that if she wishes to protect her little corner of the earth, then she cannot just sit passively defending Easthedge Nation. The whole of the Light Kingdom must be her battlefield, and her one and only home.
name: Agate Fish Ball

descr: An energetic, chipper young lady full of self-confidence and bravery. She is a dashing, formidable figure on the battlefield, and she can mix it up with the ordinary folk off the battlefield. Every day, she's like a little ball of sunshine. Moreover, Chicken on Lotus Leaf has a straightforward personality and is a touch naive, which one could say is the natural enemy of pompous pride.
name: Chicken on Lotus Leaf

descr: A young man who looks after animals like they were children. Although usually projecting an image of incorruptible impartiality, in private he buries his head in his dog's fur and gives him kisses. If anyone says his dog is ugly, he will argue with them with extreme earnestness, dead set on getting the person to sincerely admit that his dog is cute.
name: Wolfberry Decoction

descr: An inventor with an eccentric personality who's always slumped over and listless, which makes people worry about his health. With his rotten personality though, the only thing people get in return for their concern is a cold shoulder and even curses. When it comes to inventing and creating, he is extremely self-conceited, but before people that he likes, he is incredibly self-abasing.
name: Rotini

descr: Baked Apple is the scribe of the Nether Library. Scraping vellum paper, grinding minerals for pigments, and studying how to produce handmade copies—that is her daily work. Baked Apple has an eidetic memory, a prodigy, although only in feats of memory. She'll often get big-headed about her abilities, and then screw things up royally. She's scared of people hitting her head, and she protects her "apple beret" very fastidiously. According to her, her superhuman memory resides in her apple beret, and if it gets knocked off, she'll lose her memory and become an idiot.
name: French Baked Apples

descr: Sunny, cheerful, and kind, and lives in a detective agency, even though deduction isn't his strong suit. Because he trusts others too much and believes everyone is kind, he's always unable to complete missions and even makes lots of foolish blunders. Every time this happens, Mocha lends a hand, or else it might cost Latte his life. Even though his body is mostly machine, he's still determined to develop muscle that he has no chance of growing. While he feels Mocha's biceps, he fantasizes to himself how nice it would be if they were his own muscles.
name: Latte

descr: Riesling, the Head Librarian of Nether Library, is a Food Soul of considerable might possessing outstanding fighting and leadership skills. The people of Savoy call her "Gunfire Queen", while the nobles all fear her and rarely go near the library. Although she's tough and domineering on the outside, Riesling isn't a merciless tyrant at all, just a little hardheaded and inflexible. If one patiently tries to communicate with her, they'll find out she's actually a kind person.
name: Riesling

descr: Yobuko Ika possesses a white powder that can change a human's appearance, and many a young lady has made a deal with him to become more beautiful. The price was to voluntarily sacrifice something dear to them. After a young lady applied the white powder, her face would transform based on the existing foundation. If Yobuko Ika was dissatisfied with her face, he would go back on his word, and the woman would instantly become disfigured. The Proprietress invited him to join Hearsay Pavilion in order to attract more young maidens to listen to stories. Meanwhile, he became a double agent moving in and out of several main Food Soul forces in order to get revenge on behalf of his Attendant.
name: Yobuko Ika

descr: Although a sufferer of social anxiety, he will force himself to smile and socialize in order to not be hated by others. He can work tirelessly to accomplish things, but his work always gets postponed or messed up due to all kinds of accidents. He doesn't want others to call him useless trash, so his twisted psychology drives him to want to silence them for good. He always comes to his senses at the final moment, and he cries maudlin tears before his bound-up victims before running away, but he has still become a wanted criminal. However, under normal circumstances, Panini has no memory of his out-of-control states, and occasionally he'll feel hurt or confused when a former victim looks at him with fear.
name: Panini

descr: He flatters himself as capable of heartless cruelty, but his inner soft side always gives in to pure kindness, keeping him from becoming a "perfect" assassin. Even though he knows he's unable to decide or change many things, he still wants to protect others as much as he can. He despises the conditions he used to live in, and so he likes frigid, cold places. He also likes penguins and thinks it's incredible that such adorable creatures can exist in such harsh conditions.
name: Mocha

descr: This innocent and cheerful young mistress of the observatory enjoys studying astrological phenomena. Her personality is pure and kind, and she takes joy in helping others.
