She ought to have lots of friends, but at some point in the past, she drove people away from her because of her tendency to be a jinx. Later, she learned from the observatory director Monaka how to bring others good luck by making reverse wishes.
name: Konpeito

descr: The first Food Soul created by the God of Beginnings, he is without a shred of wicked impurity, an emissary of the gods representing ultimate goodness. However, due to being overly pure, Feteer is ignorant in the ways of the world and can be excessively stubborn and even crazy in some respects. After the God of Beginnings fell into a deep slumber, he took on all authority on the god's behalf. However, instead of protecting the world's people, Feteer believes he should perfect himself first. He needs to learn to love one person before he can love the whole world.
name: Feteer

descr: A Food Soul born of wicked thoughts, created by the God of Beginnings in order to maintain balance in the world. He was condemned to death for disobeying the God of Beginnings, but then he was merged into the god's thought by Feteer for selfish motives. He bitterly hates this world controlled by the God of Beginnings, and he also hates having no self because of the god, which makes him too reliant on Feteer. This is why he's made up his mind to annihilate this world and create everything anew himself.
name: Mulukhiyah

descr: Formerly a well-trained assassin, under the surface he actually has an extremely tender and thoughtful personality, the polar opposite of his bearing when on a mission. Although he likes taking care of comrades and making tasty food for everyone back at camp compared to blood and slaughter, his powerful inborn abilities have left him no choice but to be his organization's keenest weapon. He used to believe that killing was a way to correct the world and keep it orderly, but after a certain incident, he started to reevaluate its true significance and now looks for other ways to find and safeguard the life he wants.
name: Knafeh

descr: This battle queen has an undeniably imposing aura, but it's suppressed by an even more powerful force, as she is just a puppet queen. In order to shed herself of this hypocritical ruler, she risked her life to put her own dangerous plan into action. She's normally haughty and aloof, an elegant monarch not given to frivolity; but when things don't go as she anticipates—even if it's just the little prince going to bed an hour later than he should—she'll fly into a stormy rage.
name: Koshary

descr: With his high emotional IQ, he can quickly get along with the people around him. Sometimes, he even seems to be a bit crafty, but in reality he's a pure-hearted good guy. Having experienced extreme poverty and been through many hardships, he swore to become a super rich guy who would never have to know embarrassment or struggle again. Because of this, he's working hard at the Epicure Association to fulfill his goal of being promoted from intern to full-time employee.
name: Korn

descr: He may look elegant and handsome on the outside, but he's quite the deep thinker, adept at seeing into the minds of others but keeping them guessing. He's a playwright who has traveled all over and a man of high literary attainment. No one knows about his past, but he currently resides in Spring Melody Theater. He is the one truly running the show there.
name: Yuan Yang Chicken Congee

descr: The number one actor in the Light Kingdom, the leading light of the Spring Melody Theater, and its spiritual leader. He has his own beliefs and insights into the craft of traditional opera and has extremely strict demands on himself. In everyday life, he comports himself with hyperborean indifference, but in reality, he's quite pure-hearted. Inside he has a softness that he doesn't let on to others. When he takes the stage though, it's like he becomes a totally different person. His style and charm is unforgettable.
name: Goat Tripe

descr: Spring Melody Theater's pipa player. He may be a bit young, but his pipa skills are exquisite. He's also a person beloved by everyone in the theater. He has a lively and adorable personality, and people often say, "Hearing Xiao Diao Pear Soup speak is just as delightful and soothing as hearing him play the pipa."
name: Xiao Diao Pear Soup

descr: Luzhu Huoshao is the guardian of Spring Melody Theater. Normally, he's responsible for ensuring the safety of the theater. He's a worry-free, hot-blooded young man who thinks simple thoughts. He often makes jokes because of his frank openness. He is accustomed to solving problems with his sword, but his sword will only swing for people that he trusts and identifies with.
name: Luzhu Huoshao

descr: He possesses a genius mind and noble, wise looks; but in day-to-day life, he's a bumbling fool. He possesses super logical deduction capabilities and learning ability. He's also extremely sensitive to numbers and can see through superficial appearances of things to find the hidden truth within. After his former Attendant was killed by the Holy Church, he fell on hard times. He was taken under the wing by Million Dollar Stew, and currently he does odd jobs at Spring Melody Theater.
name: Yanduxian
